(8, 8237, '#', NULL, '<p><strong>Extra-marital relationship or plurality of sexual relationship </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ascendant indicates the mental set-up of the native. If planets that are negatively excited influence Ascendant they will force the native to involve in unsocial acts. If these planets simultaneously form relationship with the 7th or the 9th house (9th being the 3rd from 7th is the house of multiplications of 7th house signification) the person will involve in sexual intrigues. In general, when planets in Ascendant are not finding the sign rising on the Ascendant to be in accordance with their positive attributes, they will by their aspect on the 7th house cause for disturbed married life.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sun and Mars in Aries cause for sexual intrigues because of their acquiring more than normal passion or sexual instincts. Similarly, if Ascendant lord is Lord is under the influence of Mars, Saturn or negatively excited Moon or Venus and it establishes relationship with 7th or 9th house the native may involve in extra - marital relationships. The influence is more pronounced if the Ascendant lord is placed in 1st 5th or 7th house.</p>', '1', '2020-11-06 19:04:36.358649', '2020-11-06 19:29:49.102111'),
(9, 8856, '#', NULL, '<p>Change Alert: Jupiter changes its position from Saggi to Capricorn on 20 Nov. 2020.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Since the debilitated Jupiter will be in conjuction with the slow moving planet, Saturn, this won&#39;t be a good sign. As per me, the pandemic will be much intense after this date, hence please take care f ur health &amp; be extra vigilant.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Keep praying for a better time ahead!<br />\r\nॐ बृं बृहस्पतये नम:</p>', '1', '2020-11-09 18:40:08.765736', '2020-11-09 19:27:07.008868'),
(10, 18, '#', NULL, '<p>If you are going through Rahu Mahadasha, Antardasha or any sub-period. There will certainly some sort of anxiety and restlessness, especially if your Moon is placed with Rahu in Lagna chart or navamsa chart.&nbsp;<br />\r\nThe spiritual tip to handle it is to be in the present moment. Rahu gives insecurity with respect to the future which may not always come true.&nbsp;<br />\r\nIf you are in the present moment then you will immediately feel the difference. All anxiety and restlessness will vanish away.&nbsp;<br />\r\nJust do your routine work and whenever future insecurities come in your mind then just say &quot;Dekha jayega (Will see in future)&quot; and leave it. It has a tremendous impact and your entire Rahu Dasha will be smoothly passed. Rahu is an illusionary planet, works more at the mental level, playing with our insecurity but can be controlled easily if we surrender our future to God rather than worrying about it. &nbsp;</p>', '1', '2020-11-10 08:15:21.315908', '2020-11-10 08:16:21.913173'),
(11, 18, '#', NULL, '<p>Out of all of the consultations taken by me, 90% of those are from people who are struggling with one thing or the other. Some of them are tired of battling and resisting. Some of them are on the crossroad, they don&#39;t know what to do.&nbsp;<br />\r\nYes, Life can be hard, life can be a struggle. The truth is, that&#39;s what life is about. As long as we are working towards accomplishing anything, there are going to be obstacles.<br />\r\nEveryone faces the struggle of one or other type. Saturn, Mars, Rahu, Ketu planets are having negative energies and they will be positioned in some or other houses of the chart. There is no person whose chart does not have these planets, which means everyone will be affected by it in one area or the other area. The only thing is when it will manifest its impact and magnitude. Means when you will go through their dashas or time period. Earlier their time period, it is better, because you evolve out of it and becomes a better person for your future.&nbsp;<br />\r\nBut the truth is that everyone in one point or another point of their life will feel the struggle in one or other area of their life.&nbsp;<br />\r\nI believe more in karmic remedies or spiritual remedies because these give an everlasting impact. Secondly, whenever you do the astrological remedies, you are just postponing its impact but eventually, the planet will show the impact. With karmic and spiritual remedies, you are transforming your karma and yourself.&nbsp;<br />\r\nLearn to understand that many of struggles may not really struggle but challenges, which you can resolve in the same manner as we solve question papers in the exam. There is a need to change the perspective and solution will itself emerge in front of you. &nbsp;</p>', '1', '2020-11-14 07:53:58.583668', '2020-11-14 07:56:52.592487'),
(12, 9366, '#', NULL, '<p><strong>Transit of Sun from Libra to Scorpio on 16th November 2020</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sun is going to transit from Libra to Scorpio on 16th November 2020. Sun will remain in Scorpio till 15 December 2020 that is for a period of one month. He is going to transit from an enemy sign to a friend&rsquo;s sign as Mars and Sun are thick friends. This gives general benefit to all the people. Let us see the implications of this transit according to the Lagnam (Ascendant) and Rasi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Aries Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi</strong>: Lord of the Fifth House (House of Prosperity) Sun transiting to the Ashtamasthan (Eighth House - House of Death) reduces prosperity. Business gains will come down. Problems from children will crop up. Relations will break down. Lovers will become ex-lovers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Taurus Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi</strong>: Lord of the Fourth House (House of Comforts) Sun transiting in the Seventh house (House of marriage and business) augurs well for married life, family comforts, personal life, business profits and peace of mind. Property deals will be successful. Real estate transactions will boom. You will buy new vehicles. However, transit Ketu in Scorpio can nullify all these things depending on other planets&rsquo; placements and aspects.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Gemini Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi</strong>: Lord of the Third House (House of Courage and Efforts) Sun transiting in the Sixth House (House of Health) has no special effects. Third house (House of courage and efforts) is half Dusthana (Bad Place) and Sixth House (House of Health) is fully a Dusthana (Bad Place). You will have no benefits here and the existing problems will continue. However, one new good thing is that you will get the courage and confidence to face any challenges. You will not be cowed down by the enemies. Whether you win or not, you will fight. Speech, communication skills and argument skill will develop.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Cancer Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi</strong>: Lord of the Second House (House of Wealth, Family) Sun transiting in the Fifth house (House of prosperity) is excellent for wealth and prosperity. Financial gains will pour in. Business profit will increase. Promotions will come. Increments will be granted in the office. Foreign assignments will come. Married life will be happy. Family unity will increase. Peace of mind and happiness will set in. Relations will bloom. Ex-lovers will unite. Divorce petitions will be withdrawn. However, transit Ketu in Scorpio can nullify all these things depending on other planets&rsquo; placements and aspects.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Leo Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi</strong>: Lagnatipati (Lord of the Ascendant) Sun transiting in the Fourth house (House of comforts) is beneficial for family unity, happiness, peace, comforts, luxuries and satisfaction. New property deals will come. You will buy new vehicles. New deals will be struck. New friendship will be developed. However, transit Ketu in Scorpio can nullify all these things depending on other planets&rsquo; placements and aspects.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Virgo Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi</strong>: Lord of the Twelfth House (House of Losses) Sun transiting in the Third house (House of courage and efforts) does not benefit. Existing problems will continue. Confidence and courage will go down. Fear will grip the mind. Efforts will be in vain. Losses will come without announcement.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Libra Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi</strong>: Lord of the Eleventh House (House of Gains) Sun transiting in the Second house (House of wealth and family) augurs well for the wealth and financial gains. New ventures will fetch reward. New friends will develop. Wishes will be fulfilled. Wealth will multiply. Family will be happy. Lovers will unite. Marriages will be fixed. However, transit Ketu in Scorpio can nullify all these things depending on other planets&rsquo; placements and aspects.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Scorpio Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi</strong>: Lord of the Tenth House (House of Profession) Sun transiting in the Lagnam (Ascendant) brings professional and career gains. Your efforts will be rewarded and appreciated in the office. Promotions will come. Increments will be granted. Foreign assignments will come. However, transit Ketu in Scorpio can nullify all these things depending on other planets&rsquo; placements and aspects. Sudden heart attack can happen in the next one month because of the association of Ketu and Sun.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Sagittarius Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi</strong>: Lord of the Ninth House (House of Fortune) Sun transiting in the Twelfth house (House of losses) with Ketu is not good. Opportunities will be missed. Fortunes will be lost. Spirituality will increase. Foreign trips will be cancelled or prove to be unprofitable. Higher studies will be affected.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Capricorn Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi</strong>: Ashtamatipati (Lord of the Eighth House) Sun transiting in the Eleventh house (House of gains) does not augur well for financial gains. Friendship will break. Relations will break. Lovers will become ex-lovers. Wishes will not be fulfilled.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Aquarius Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi</strong>: Lord of the Seventh House (House of Marriage) Sun transiting in the Tenth house (House of profession) will be very good for business ventures. Profits will zoom. Expansion, modernization and diversification will occur in business houses. However, transit Ketu in Scorpio can nullify all these things depending on other planets&rsquo; placements and aspects.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Pisces Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi</strong>: Lord of the Sixth House (House of Health) Sun transiting in the Ninth house (House of fortune) can damage opportunities and wreck fortunes. Students will not get good results in higher education examination. However, those who appear for competitive examinations like NEET, IIT etc will gain.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Who will gain the most? Those who have Cancer Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi and having a natal Sun in Scorpio gain a lot as they have a double Sun effect. Financial gains will be huge for them. Instead of Cancer Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi, if the Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi is Libra, then also the same benefit will come.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Who will be affected a lot? Those who have Capricorn Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi and have natal Sun or Ketu in Scorpio will be affected a lot as they will face a double Ketu or double Sun (this means a double Ashtamatipati (Lord of the Eighth House)) effect that will be too much for them to bear.</p>', '1', '2020-11-16 22:04:13.516512', '2020-11-17 11:53:38.628259'),
(13, 8237, '#', NULL, '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Promise for Marriage and connection of Navansha D-9 Chart&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nNavamsha is specific chart for marriage related matters.It can be seen independently for analysing marriage of a person.<br />\r\nExamination:<br />\r\n1. Lagna of Navamsha is the major consideration for marriage. A strong Lagna and Lagna lord gives marriage.<br />\r\n2. Wealth and speech in marriage. It also shows longivity of spouse. An efflicted second house is not welcome as it gives tensions in married life.<br />\r\n3. The conflicts and problems faced in marriage. A strong 6th house has no conflicts and the married life is smooth.<br />\r\n4. Intelligence of married life. It is the thought process one has towards marriage. An efflicted 5th house carries bad intentions and is a spark to ruin the marriage. A benefic 5th house can avert an ugly situation.<br />\r\n5. All about marriage partner. A well connected 7th house gives a good life partner.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Promise of Marriage:</strong><br />\r\nLagna of Navamsha is the primary consideration. If the lagna has a benefic or is aspected by benefic then marriage is assured. Second house and seventh house are next consideration. These houses should also have benefic association. Association with lord of the house even when a malefic is considered good.<br />\r\nWhen all three i.e. lagna, second house and seventh house have malefic association then marriage is denied or delayed.<br />\r\nAnother method is to look for the seventh lord/lagna lord of birth chart in navamsha. If these lords are badly placed in 2,6,8,12 houses from birth lagna&nbsp; and from the sign occupied by it in birth chart or in navamsha, then marriage is denied. When well placed from one of these signs, it gives marriage but with problems in married life.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Affliction to Venus is also hinderance to marriage.Venus in strength and well placed in birth chart and navansha assures marriage</strong>.</p>', '0', '2020-11-17 11:08:29.301126', '2020-11-17 11:55:03.785856'),
(14, 8237, '#', NULL, '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>High Energy and Passionate Mars Moon Combination</strong>:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Moon conjunct Mars </strong>in the natal astrology chart gives an emotionally passionate astrology nature. These people have a zest for life and their infectious energy can rouse the passions of others. They wear their heart on their sleeve and it is healthier for them to share how they feel. In fact they may find it difficult not to let their strong emotions out, which has given this astrology aspect a reputation of giving emotional rashness and a hot temper.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBut this is simply a side effect of having such enthusiasm and astrology energy for life. These sexy lovers and fierce fighters need a constructive outlet for their passions so the hot energy doesn&rsquo;t turn in and destructive. Dramatic emotional displays are a good astrology thing, sometimes.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThere is a astrology bluntness and straightforwardness to these people that is unmistakable. Although they are completely ready to defend and protect their loved ones, they are not especially sympathetic on a more personal astrology level. They&rsquo;ll most definitely defend the &ldquo;weak&rdquo;, but they are too emotionally excitable, self-absorbed, and brusque to be considered gentle and sympathetic astrology folk! They&rsquo;re brave and they value personal freedom. Astrology routine bores them, and they are inclined to seek out excitement in some form. Spontaneous to a fault, these people react quickly to stimuli. They are usually physically resilient. Their astrology temper is quick, but it can disappear just as rapidly. Theirs is a raw astrology passion.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '0', '2020-11-17 11:13:58.130402', '2020-11-17 11:55:09.762001'),
(15, 8237, '#', NULL, '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Promise for Marriage connection of Navamsha D-9 Chart&nbsp; Navansha</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nNavamsha is specific chart for marriage related matters.It can be seen independently for analysing marriage of a person.<br />\r\nExamination:<br />\r\n1. Lagna of Navamsha is the major consideration for marriage. A strong Lagna and Lagna lord gives marriage.<br />\r\n2. Wealth and speech in marriage. It also shows longivity of spouse. An efflicted second house is not welcome as it gives tensions in married life.<br />\r\n3. The conflicts and problems faced in marriage. A strong 6th house has no conflicts and the married life is smooth.<br />\r\n4. Intelligence of married life. It is the thought process one has towards marriage. An efflicted 5th house carries bad intentions and is a spark to ruin the marriage. A benefic 5th house can avert an ugly situation.<br />\r\n5. All about marriage partner. A well connected 7th house gives a good life partner.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nLagna of Navamsha is the primary consideration. If the lagna has a benefic or is aspected by benefic then marriage is assured. Second house and seventh house are next consideration. These houses should also have benefic association. Association with lord of the house even when a malefic is considered good.<br />\r\nWhen all three i.e. lagna, second house and seventh house have malefic association then marriage is denied or delayed.<br />\r\nAnother method is to look for the seventh lord/lagna lord of birth chart in navamsha. If these lords are badly placed in 2,6,8,12 houses from birth lagna&nbsp; and from the sign occupied by it in birth chart or in navamsha, then marriage is denied. When well placed from one of these signs, it gives marriage but with problems in married life.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nAffliction to Venus is also hinderance to marriage.Venus in strength and well placed in birth chart and navansha assures marriage.</p>', '0', '2020-