(17, 8237, '#', NULL, '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Promise for Marriage connection of Navamsha D-9 Chart&nbsp; Navansha</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nWe review D-9 Navansha chart for marriage . &nbsp;This chart can be seen independently also for marriage analysis:<br />\r\n1. Navamsha lagan is the major consideration for marriage. A strong Lagna and Lagna lord gives marriage.<br />\r\n2. Wealth and speech .It also shows longivity of spouse. An efflicted second house is not welcome as it gives tensions in married life.<br />\r\n3. The conflicts and problems faced in marriage life . A powerful 6th house has no conflicts and the married life is smooth.<br />\r\n4. Intelligence of married life. Thought process one has towards marriage. An efflicted 5th house carries bad intentions and is a spark to ruin the marriage. A benefic 5th house can avert an ugly situation.<br />\r\n5. All about marriage partner. A strong connected &nbsp;7th house gives a good life partner.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNavansha lagana is the primary consideration. If the lagna has a benefic planet &nbsp;or is aspected by benefic &nbsp;planet then marriage is assured. 2nd house and seventh house are next consideration. These houses should also have benefic association. Association with lord of the 2nd and 7th house even when a malefic is considered good.<br />\r\nWhen all three i.e. lagna, second house and seventh house have malefic planets and aspected by malefics &nbsp;then marriage is denied or delayed.<br />\r\nAnother method is to look for the seventh lord and lagna lord of birth chart in navamsha. If these lords are placed in 2,6,8,12 houses from birth lagna&nbsp; and from the sign occupied by it in birth chart or in navamsha, then marriage is denied.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Affliction to Venus is also hinderance to marriage.Venus in strength and well placed in birth chart and navansha assures marriage.</p>', '1', '2020-11-17 13:40:24.538270', '2020-11-17 18:15:31.036503'),
(18, 8237, '#', NULL, '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>10th house of profession and source of Income.</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe 10th is the most powerful Kendra. Strong planets gives a person a good profession. Benefic planets make a native generous. A benefic in 10th from lagna or Moon gives rise to Amla yoga and yoga of nobility and prosperity. According Phaladeepika when a benefic planet is placed in the 10th house or if Lord of 10th house is placed in Kendra or trikona in its own sign or sign of exaltation or when lord of lagna is in the 10th house one becomes very famous and does meritourous deeds.<br />\r\nAccording to Varahmir see (10th from Lagna, Moon and Sun) and find out which is strongest of the three. This would show profession. The source of wealth would be as follows. This also applies to lord of the D-9 &nbsp;10th lord if there is no planet in the 10th. Out of three, Lagna , Moon, or Sun the planet whosoever is strongest will suggest the profession. If it is :<br />\r\nSun : State services administration and management. A strong Sun in the 10th house, aspects by benefics raises person to great social, political and economic heights by his own effort.<br />\r\nA week Sun aspected by malefics leads to many obstacles and frustrations in life.<br />\r\nConnection of Sun with Saturn is not good combination, and causes difficulties in career especially if Sun is within 7 degrees of Saturn. Good aspect of Saturn makes one a high government officer.<br />\r\nMoon : Exalted Moon in 10 as a lord of 12 means income from&nbsp; exports. Get wealth and recognition from the state, gain from women from high family .As the Moon is female planet and indicates females, women might be having some influence over him or he may get wealth from his mother.<br />\r\nA good degree of Moon indicates stable career or longevity in career no breaks. But if the Moon is afflicted or less degree than the person has to face lot of Job changes no stability in career.<br />\r\nJupiter : Legal work, religious preaching, classical and religious learning, teaching, Banker.<br />\r\nSaturn : Saturn in 10 without benefic aspect means frustrated career. Affliction with Mercury menial jobs. Saturn and Mars in 10th house aspected by Moon and Jupiter manufacturing industry.<br />\r\nRahu-Venus : Many Lovers. It is also combination for computer engineering. Electronics Engineering IT.<br />\r\nKetu : Foreign languages, Computers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '1', '2020-11-17 13:50:50.139654', '2020-11-17 18:13:27.037399'),
(19, 9366, '#', NULL, '<p><strong>Transit of Venus from Virgo to Libra on 17th November 2020</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Venus has transited from Virgo to Libra on 17th November 2020. This is a good transit as Venus has entered into his own House Libra, where he will be powerful. Therefore, the benefits will be more and the harm will be less. Here, Venus will remain till December 11 2020- around 25 days. Venus will be with Mercury in Libra till November 28 2020. During this time (that is from 17th November 2020 to 28th November 2020), the benefits will be more as Mercury and Venus are thick friends and both of them are residing in Venus&rsquo; own house Libra. We will now see the implications of this transit based on the individual Lagnam (Ascendant) and Rasi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Aries Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi</strong>: Lord of the Second House (House of Wealth, Family) Venus transiting in the Seventh house (House of marriage and business) is good for business profits, married life and relationship. Ex-lovers will be united again. Divorce petition will be withdrawn. Wealth will increase. Lord of the Seventh House (House of Marriage) Venus in the Seventh house (House of marriage and business) will make women visit their mothers&rsquo; house and stay there for around a month. Married women will receive benefits from their parents.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Taurus Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi</strong>: Lagnatipati (Lord of the Ascendant) Venus transiting in the Sixth House (House of Health) invites obstacles, troubles, court cases, arrests, dismissal from service, vigilance cases in the office, huge debt burden, financial problems, injuries, illnesses, surgeries, medical expenses and other troubles. Lord of the Sixth House (House of Health) Venus transiting in the Sixth House (House of Health) also invites the same troubles stated above.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Gemini Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi</strong>: Lord of the Twelfth House (House of Losses) Venus in the Fifth house (House of prosperity) brings losses in business, career and personal life. It also brings frequent visit to doctors and hospitals. However, married life will be happy. Relations will bloom. Ex-lovers will be united. Lord of the Fifth House (House of Prosperity) Venus transiting in the Fifth house (House of prosperity) enhances your prosperity and benefits your children also. Relationship will bloom. Ex-lovers will be united. Speculation will reward like stock market investment.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Cancer Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi</strong>: Lord of the Eleventh House (House of Gains) Venus transiting in the Fourth house (House of comforts) brings financial gains, family comforts, luxuries, new houses and new vehicles. Lord of the Fourth House (House of Comforts) Venus in the Fourth house (House of comforts) brings benefits of new properties, real estate and expanding the existing houses.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Leo Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi</strong>: Lord of the Tenth House (House of Profession) Venus transiting in the Third house (House of courage and efforts) makes your efforts in career and business a waste. Efforts will not be rewarded. Promotions will be given to other people who are inferior to you in the organization. Laziness will set in. Mental tension will set in. Lord of the Third House (House of Courage and Efforts) Venus transiting in the Third house (House of courage and efforts) raises your courage and confidence to take up the challenges.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Virgo Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi</strong>: Lord of the Ninth House (House of Fortune) Venus transiting in the Second house (House of wealth and family) brings fortunes, opportunities, spiritualism, family pleasures and many other things. Lord of the Second House (House of Wealth, Family) Venus transiting in the Second house (House of wealth and family) enhances your wealth and family unity.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Libra Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi</strong>: Ashtamatipati (Lord of the Eighth House) Venus in the Lagnam (Ascendant) brings injuries, illnesses, accidents, surgeries and other harm. You should be very careful. Lagnatipati (Lord of the Ascendant) Venus in the Lagnam (Ascendant) protects you from the above harmful things and saves your life.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Scorpio Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi</strong>: Lord of the Seventh House (House of Marriage) Venus transiting in the Twelfth house (House of losses) brings disputes in the married life. Divorce petitions will be filed. Lovers will quarrel and part ways apart. Business will be affected. Huge losses will come. Spouse will get sick or injuries and will have to frequently visit hospitals and doctors. Medical bills will shoot up. Lord of the Twelfth House (House of Losses) Venus transiting in the Twelfth house (House of losses) makes married life happy. However, you will have to visit hospitals frequently for your own health concerns. Sudden foreign trips will materialise. Students will get visa to study abroad. Employees will get foreign postings or new jobs abroad.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Sagittarius Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi</strong>: Lord of the Sixth House (House of Health) Venus in the Eleventh house (House of gains) reduces financial gains. Friendship will be broken. Wishes will not be fulfilled. Plans will fail. Efforts will go waste. Relations will break. Lord of the Eleventh House (House of Gains) in the Eleventh house (House of gains) brings Parijatha Yoga (that brings financial prosperity). This gives financial prosperity and happiness. It will be therefore, a mixed period for you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Capricorn Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi</strong>: Lord of the Fifth House (House of Prosperity) Venus in the Tenth house (House of profession) brings prosperity through profession. Lord of the Tenth House (House of Profession) Venus transiting in the Tenth house (House of profession) also enhances prosperity through profession. Career will boom. Promotions and increments will come. Foreign postings will come. Lot of financial gains will come.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Aquarius Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi:</strong> Lord of the Fourth House (House of Comforts) Venus transiting in the Ninth house (House of fortune) is good for family comforts, luxuries, properties and vehicles. Lord of the Ninth House (House of Fortune) Venus in the Ninth house (House of fortune) brings new opportunities, fortunes and raises spiritualism</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Pisces Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi</strong>: Lord of the Third House (House of Courage and Efforts) Venus transiting in the Ashtamasthan (Eighth House - House of Death) brings no benefits. Existing problems will continue. New problems may also crop up. Courage and confidence will be lost. Laziness will set in. Ashtamatipati (Lord of the Eighth House) Venus transiting in Ashtamasthan (Eighth House - House of Death) can invite suicidal tendencies, love failures, injuries, illnesses and surgeries. Accidents can happen.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Who will benefit from the above transit the most</strong>? If a person has Virgo Lagnam (Ascendant) and Rasi and has the natal Venus placed in the Second house (House of wealth and family) Libra, then it will give him excellent results because it is tantamount to a double Venus benefits.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Who will be affected the most</strong>? Those who have Pisces Lagnam (Ascendant) as well as Rasi and natal Venus in Libra will have to face a double Ashtamatipati (Lord of the Eighth House) in the Ashtamasthan (Eighth House - House of Death) that is really a grueling experience.&nbsp;</p>', '1', '2020-11-21 01:07:44.524811', '2020-11-21 17:53:40.524694'),
(20, 9366, '#', NULL, '<p><strong>Transit of Jupiter from Sagittarius to Capricorn on 20-11-2020</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Out of all the transits, Jupiter transit is the most looked for and most exciting. This is because the benefits or harm from the transit of minor planets are only for a short time &ndash; at the most one month or one and a half months. Among the major planets, Rahu and Ketu transits are feared because of the harm that they may do to the people. It is a question of less harm or more harm. Saturn transit is also dreaded as that can also produce harm. However, Jupiter transit generally favours the people. It is a question of more favours or less favours. More than the question of from which place to which place Jupiter transits, his aspects are very important. Jupiter has three aspects namely fifth aspect, straight seventh aspect and ninth aspect. These aspects can boost one&rsquo;s career, finances, business, marriage, health, family, personal life, courage, confidence, property acquisition, vehicle acquisition, comforts, luxuries, children&rsquo;s education, academics, higher studies, foreign settlement, foreign education, debt, court cases, long pending marriage, love relationships, spirituality, fortunes, opportunities, promotions, rewards in work place, fulfillment of wishes, friendship, minimizing losses, sex life, recovery from diseases and many such points. Jupiter will remain in Capricorn till November 21 2021. In between, he will come back to Sagittarius and then go again to Capricorn. The next one year period is very important for all the people in the world. Here, I have given my analysis of the benefits for each Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi for the next one year. As Jupiter has two Lordships, I have analyzed both. For good results, I have used blue text and for bad results I have used red text. If the result is neither good nor bad, I have used black text. This will be useful for the readers to analyze the outcome at a glance easily. Also remember that the transit Jupiter is going to be debilitated in Capricorn and hence will lose his powers substantially. Benefits will reduce and harm will also reduce because of this.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Aries Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi</strong>: Lord of the Ninth House (House of Fortune) Jupiter entering into the Tenth house (House of profession) creates a Dharma Karmatipati Yoga (A straightforward person with many fortunes in life and career). Fortunes will come to you. Many opportunities in career, profession, business will knock at your doors on their own. Sudden ideas will strike that prove beneficial. Foreign trips will materialise. Add to this, the benefit of your Lord of the Tenth House (House of Profession) Saturn transiting in the Tenth house (House of profession) is excellent. Jupiter aspects your Second house (House of wealth and family), Fourth house (House of comforts) and Sixth House (House of Health). Wealth will increase. Family comforts, luxuries, properties, vehicles will come. Enemies will be smashed. Diseases will be cured. Debt will be repaid.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Lord of the Twelfth House (House of Losses) Jupiter transiting in the Tenth house (House of profession) brings losses in career and business. Health problems will develop and frequent visit to hospitals and doctors will result.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Taurus Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi</strong>: Ashtamatipati (Lord of the Eighth House) Jupiter entering into the Ninth house (House of fortune) is bad for fortunes and opportunities. Spiritualism will take a beating. Mental tension will increase. Father&rsquo;s health will suffer. There will be quarrels with father.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Lord of the Eleventh House (House of Gains) Jupiter transiting in the Ninth house (House of fortune) brings fortunes, opportunities and financial gains. Wishes will be fulfilled. Friendship will develop. Foreign trips will materialise. Spiritualism will increase. Higher studies will be successful. You will get blessings from elders. Jupiter aspects your Lagnam (Ascendant), Third house (House of courage and efforts) and Fifth house (House of prosperity). You will be confident, healthy and courageous. Prosperity will pour in.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Gemini Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi</strong>: Lord of the Seventh House (House of Marriage) Jupiter entering into Ashtamasthan (Eighth House - House of Death) is bad for married life. Divorce petitions may be filed. Business will take a beating. Business losses will mount up. Business partners will separate after quarreling.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Lord of the Tenth House (House of Profession) transiting in the Ashtamasthan (Eighth House - House of Death) brings bad things to the career, profession and jobs. Jobs may be lost. Salaries may be cut. Vigilance enquiries may be initiated. Increments will be cut. Foreign jobs will be lost. Opportunities will be missed. Fortunes will be lost.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Cancer Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi</strong>: Lord of the Sixth House (House of Health) Jupiter transiting in the Seventh house (House of marriage and business) breaks married life. Divorce petitions will be filed. Relations will break. Lovers will become ex-lovers. Business will break down. Losses will mount. Business partners will quarrel and separate. Court cases may be filed. Arrests may be made. Huge debt will depress and cause mental tension.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Lord of the Ninth House (House of Fortune) Jupiter transiting in the Seventh house (House of marriage and business) brings opportunities for marriage. Unmarried people will get suitable alliances. Fortunes will increase after marriage. Business fortunes will increase. Business opportunities will open up. New relations will come. Boys and girls searching for suitable partners for love relation will get it this time. Jupiter aspects your Eleventh house (House of gains), Lagnam (Ascendant) and Third house (House of courage and efforts). Financial gains will flow. Friendship will boom. Wishes will be fulfilled. You will be strong and healthy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Leo Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi</strong>: Lord of the Fifth House (House of Prosperity) Jupiter transiting in the Sixth House (House of Health) makes prosperity down. Children will have problems in education and health. Children may fall and sustain fracture and injuries. Stock market investment will give losses.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ashtamatipati (Lord of the Eighth House) Jupiter transiting in the Sixth House (House of Health) can cause injuries, illnesses, accidents and surgeries. Debt will mount. Enemies will create problems. Black magic may be performed. Financial problems will be depressing. Mental tension will force suicidal tendencies.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Virgo Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi</strong>: Lord of the Fourth House (House of Comforts) Jupiter transiting in the Fifth house (House of prosperity) brings prosperity, family comforts, luxuries, children&rsquo;s happiness, assistance from children and relatives. Stock market investments will give profits. Transit Jupiter aspects your Ninth house (House of fortune), Eleventh house (House of gains) and your Lagnam (Ascendant). Fortunes will pour. Financial gains will be plenty. Friendship will develop. Opportunities will knock at your door. Foreign trip will materialise. Relations will bloom. Ex-lovers will unite. Spiritualism will increase. Higher studies will be a success. Foreign jobs will come to you easily. Students will go abroad for studies. You will be strong, healthy, confident and courageous.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Lord of the Seventh House (House of Marriage) Jupiter transiting in the Fifth house (House of prosperity) will clinch marriage deals. Lovers will marry. Parents objecting to the marriages will yield and permit such marriages. Stock market will yield enormous gains. Children will get enormous benefits in education and health. Business will boom. Business gains will be at a record level. Business people will open new branches and shops.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Libra Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi</strong>: Lord of the Third House (House of Courage and Efforts) Jupiter entering into Fourth house (House of comforts) has no special gains except courage and confidence. Brothers may create problems and ask for their share of your prosperity. Brothers may fight and go to the courts. Family comforts and luxuries will come down. Property deals will end up in problems. Purchase of vehicles will be postponed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Lord of the Sixth House (House of Health) Jupiter entering into the Fourth house (House of comforts) damages family comforts and luxuries. Property deals will be stuck up. Purchase of new vehicles will pose problems. Mother&rsquo;s health will take a beating. There may be quarrels with the mother.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Scorpio Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi</strong>: Lord of the Second House (House of Wealth, Family) Jupiter entering into the Third house (House of courage and efforts) has no special benefits for you. Third house (House of courage and efforts) is half Dusthana (Bad Place). Wealth may come down. Unnecessary expenses may crop up. Family atmosphere may be damaged.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Lord of the Fifth House (House of Prosperity) Jupiter transiting in the Third house (House of courage and efforts) has no special benefits for you. Prosperity will come down. Children may have problems with health and education. Stock market gains will be wiped out and losses may happen. Relations will be affected. Lovers may become ex-lovers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Sagittarius Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi</strong>: Lagnatipati (Lord of the Ascendant) Jupiter transiting in the Second house (House of wealth and family) brings wealth and family happiness to you. Speech and communication will increase to your benefit. Teachers will be rewarded for their good teaching. Transit Jupiter aspects your Sixth House (House of Health), Eighth House (House of Death) and Tenth house (House of profession). Profession, career and job will shine. You will be recognized for your work in the organization. Enemies will walk away from you fearing retribution. Injuries, illness, diseases will suddenly disappear. You will be in the pink of health. Research students will succeed during the transit. Sudden income will come pleasantly.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Lord of the Fourth House (House of Comforts) Jupiter transiting in the Second house (House of wealth and family) boosts up your family comforts, luxuries, properties, vehicles, wealth and family pleasures. You will buy new properties. You will construct new houses. Here, you are assisted by the fact that Lord of the Second House (House of Wealth, Family) Saturn is positioned in the Second house (House of wealth and family) itself in transit. Lagnatipati (Lord of the Ascendant), Lord of the Fourth House (House of Comforts) and Lord of the Second House (House of Wealth, Family) have combined to give you an excellent period of prosperity.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Capricorn Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi</strong>: Lord of the Twelfth House (House of Losses) Jupiter coming to the Lagnam (Ascendant) invites losses, health problems, frequent visit to hospitals and inflated medical bills. However, marriage life will be happy. Relations will bloom. Ex-lovers will unite. The combination of Lord of the Twelfth House (House of Losses) and Lord of the Second House (House of Wealth, Family) gives huge expenses and at the same time good income to manage the expenses. Because of these benefits, it is generally a beneficial period for you. Jupiter aspects your Fifth house (House of prosperity), Seventh house (House of marriage and business) and Ninth house (House of fortune). These aspects are beneficial. Prosperity will increase. Married life will be happy. Business will boom and produce more profits. Fortunes will increase. Opportunities will knock at the door. Spiritualism will increase. Foreign assignments will come. Students will be successful in higher studies.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Lord of the Third House (House of Courage and Efforts) transiting in the Lagnam (Ascendant) boosts up your confidence, courage and hard work. Efforts will pay good dividend. Brothers will come seeking assistance from you. They will also be helpful.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Aquarius Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi</strong>: Lord of the Eleventh House (House of Gains) Jupiter transiting in the Twelfth house (House of losses) nullifies the financial gains and converts them into losses through huge medical bills. Health problems will crop up. Frequent visit to doctors will happen. Medical bills shoot up. Friendship will be cut off. Relations will break. Lovers will become ex-lovers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Lord of the Second House (House of Wealth, Family) Jupiter transiting in the Twelfth house (House of losses) also brings the same results stated above. There will be huge and unwanted expenses to dent the wealth and force you to borrow money.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Pisces Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi</strong>: Lord of the Tenth House (House of Profession) Jupiter transiting in the Eleventh house (House of gains) is excellent. Profession will boom. Financial gains will increase. Friendship will flourish. Relations will bloom. Ex-lovers will be united. Wishes will be fulfilled. Jupiter aspects your Third house (House of courage and efforts), Fifth house (House of prosperity) and Seventh house (House of marriage and business). Courage and confidence will increase. Hard work will pay dividends. Prosperity will increase. Your children will shine in education and their health also will be good. Stock market investments will give good returns. Married life will be happy. Business will boom. Profits will increase.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Lagnatipati (Lord of the Ascendant) in the Eleventh house (House of gains) gives lot of financial gains, new friends, new relationship and grant of your wishes. Your other income will flourish apart from your professional income.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Who will benefit most from the transit?</strong> A person with Sagittarius Lagnam (Ascendant) and also Sagittarius Rasi and having his natal Jupiter placed in Cancer in an exalted position to compensate the debilitated transit Jupiter will gain a log from the transit</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Who will be affected most by the transit?</strong> Those who have Gemini Lagnam (Ascendant) and also Rasi with natal Jupiter placed in Capricorn will be affected severely as they have both their natal and transit Jupiter in their Ashtamasthan (Eighth House - House of Death)</p>', '1', '2020-11-21 01:10:52.295366', '2020-11-21 17:59:05.124491'),
(21, 3944, '#', NULL, '<p><em><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Six of cups Tarot card</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Among all 78 cards in the deck, this card is the very good card for partnership, meeting and love. It represents pure innocence connection with association of past memories. This card represent a past sweet memories weather as child, teenager or adult. This is representing your school friend, collage friend after a long break. In the figure the old men walk away a distance showing a protection and passing a message to children&rsquo;s to follow their heart. The filled four cups with flowers also indicating sense of happiness and pleasant environment.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This card represent a boy carrying a cup with a flower and offering it to a girl, this indicate his feeling of pure love towards the girl and the girl is also seeing to the boy with hope and love. The flower in cup represent love, harmony and respect of boy towards a girl. This indicating a strong and pure connection of both. It is also representing reconnection of past lovers. Overall it is very positive card in aspect of love. Although it is also representing child birth. But it is one of the very positive card regarding pure love.</p>', '1', '2020-11-22 14:49:40.569780', '2020-11-23 10:39:05.509425');
