(43, 831, '#', NULL, '<p><strong>Purva Janma ki Shaap Pida : Curses of the Past Life ( Part:2)&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>In Part One of this article ( dated 14th August 2019 on our platform), I have tried to translate and explain two commonly occurring yogas out of these six well-known inauspicious yogas in jatak&#39;s chart.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Now in this article, I have tried to explain the Four remaining Shaap Pida namely, Pitru Shaap, Pret Shaap, Anapatya Yoga and Abhichar Yoga. I have drawn the gist of this article from the original text through the reference of a Marathi book.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>According to Bruhad Parashar Hora Shatram, the aadhyay based on &quot; Purvajanma Shaapdyotak Aadhyay&quot; covers Serpa Shaap( Naga Dosha), Pitru Dosha, Anapatya Yoga, Pret Badha, Pishachya Badha and Abhichar Yoga are in very precise and easy manner.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>C. PITRU SHAAP&nbsp;: It mainly occurs in,the chart due to debilitating Sun in 5th or 9th house. This yoga become more worst if Sun in this house placed with malefic planets in 1st and 12th houses of debilitating Sun. This may result in loss of progeny or delay child birth or reduced longevity of one&#39;s child.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. If the ascendant occupied with malefic planet this result will be certain.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. There will be no child if there will any connection between 10th Mars and 5th lord and malefic planets present in ascendant, 5th and 10th houses.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. If Sun is placed in 8th house, 5th house occupied with Saturn and ascendant with malefic planet, then there will be no yoga for child in person&#39;s life.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. If the 5th house is occupied with 6th and 10th house lord and Guru placed with Rahu in any of the houses, there will be lots of chances of loss of progeny ( before and after the birth). As per the Bruhad Parashar Hora Shashtram&#39;, Narayan Bali Nag Bali pujan is must with &#39; Gaya Shraddha&#39;. Gaya Shraddha is also done in Trambkeshwar near Nashik called as &#39; Rudra Gaya&#39;. Ujjain ( M.P) is also the other auspicious placed to solve this inauspicious pujan.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>D. PRET SHAAP: In this inauspicious yoga, the karmas of past ancestors get nullified due to their incomplete last time recit. This results in difficulty and obstacles in persons current life and ahead.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. This results due to Sun- Saturn combo in 5th or 9th house specially with weak Moon in 7th house and Guru-Rahu Chandal Yoga in any of the houses in the chart.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. 5th house lord Shani placed in 8th house, ascendant is occupied with Mars and 8th house with Guru.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. Ascendant with Rahu,Venus, and Guru and 8th house occupied with Shani and Moon.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. Rahu in lagna and Shani with Mars or suspected by Mars causes the loss of progeny.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5. 8th house with Shani Venus and Guru too causes this bad yoga. As per the Bruhad Parashar Hora Shashtram&#39;, Narayan Bali Nag Bali pujan, Vishnu Shraddha, donating Brahma idol to Brahmin after Rudrabhishek.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>E. ANAPATYA YOGA ( No Child Birth) As per Bhagwat Gita - Dyaiva Chaivatra Panchmam&#39; means there is no option available for These Shaap Pida obtained due to the past lives karma of a person. King Dasharath is the best example of this Dosha. He obtained the pleasures of Four children but specially Lord Rama, but also got the seperation from his beloved Rama at the time of his death bed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. This occurs when 5th, 2nd, and 7th lord get connected anyhow by yoga or aspects of malefic in Navamash chart.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. Lord of ascendant when placed in 8th house, 5th house lord when afflicted with malefic planets and Guru in debilitating state specially in Shashtiamsha Chart.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. Weak Guru, ascendant lord 7th and 5th house lord also results in,this inauspicious yoga.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. 5th house occupied with debilitating malefic planets and ascendant as well as 5th lord may be present in either 6th or 8th or 12th house. Karak planet Guru should also be in debilitating state. As per the Bruhad Parashar Hora Shashtram&#39;, Narayan Bali Nag Bali pujan can be the remedy for this yoga.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>F. ABHICHAR YOG: Obstacle in the child birth is also due to this bad yoga.Person doesn&#39;t get the child in life or if got then faces a lots of trouble.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. This happened when Acendant is occupied with either any of the sign of Aries, Cancer, Libra or Capricorn and ascendant is expected by lord of the 6th house lord.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. 11th house Mars results in Abhichar Yoga.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. 9th house is occupied with any of the sign out of Taurus, Leo, Scorpio or Aquarius whereas, 7th house should be occupied with Gemini, Vergo, Sagittarius or Pisces As per the Bruhad Parashar Hora Shashtram&#39;, Narayan Bali Nag Bali pujan and Tripindi Shraddha. Now it can be done at Trambkeshwar near Nashik.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Best Period for these remedies are Bhadrapada Krusha Paksha ( Pitru Paksha) or Pousha Month as per the Hindu Calender.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Article Submitted by :: Acharya&nbsp;Bhushan Ratnakar.</p>', '0', '2020-12-22 14:19:43.349709', '2020-12-22 14:19:43.349709'),
(44, 9141, '#', NULL, '<p>अपने घर में सुख-शांति बनाए:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>घर में सुबह सुबह कुछ देर के लिए भक्ति गीत, भजन अवश्य करें या बजायें ।</p>\r\n\r\n<p>घर में कभी भी झाड़ू को खड़ा करके नहीं रखें, उसे पैर नहीं लगाएं, न ही उसके ऊपर से गुजरे अन्यथा घर में अलक्ष्मी निवास करने लगेगी ।</p>\r\n\r\n<p>अपने घर के पूजा स्थल में सदैव जल से भरा एक कलश जरूर रखें ।</p>\r\n\r\n<p>पूजा में उपयोग होने वाली धूप, आरती, दीप, हवन की अग्नि जैसे पवित्रता के प्रतिक साधनों को कभी भी अपने मुंह से फूंक मारकर नहीं बुझाएं ।</p>', '0', '2020-12-22 16:40:42.691661', '2020-12-22 16:40:42.691661'),
(45, 11071, '#', NULL, '<p><em><strong>Importance of tithi in panchang</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>In panchang lunar tithi&nbsp; has been&nbsp; given a great importance .These thiti&#39;s are associated with what work&nbsp; one should do according to them.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4th 6th 8th 9th and 14th tithi of either paksha are considered to be chidra (hole) tithi and are not auspicious for traveling. Even if the 14th tithi has a good nakshatara, still one must avoid traveling.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1st 6th and 11th tithi are known as nanda tithi . It is auspicious to buy new clothes , ornaments and&nbsp; also&nbsp; to enjoy good food.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2nd 7th and 12th are known as bhadhra tithi .This is considered good to join a job or take a power and chant swasthi vaachan mantras.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3rd, 8th and 13th are known as Jaya tithi . These are good to file a suit, defense related work to manufacture arms and ammunition, defense deals and good for business men to get profit by selling and purchasing goods.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4th 9th&nbsp; and14th thiti are rikta&nbsp; tithi .No&nbsp;new work should be initiated on these tithi &#39;s either of moveable Nature&nbsp; or fixed nature.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5th 10th and 15th tithi are Purana tithi .These tithi &#39;s are good for construction and development&nbsp; work.&nbsp;</p>', '1', '2020-12-22 21:39:31.900115', '2020-12-23 12:23:22.136628'),
(46, 9366, '#', NULL, '<p>Venus, the minor planet, transited from her own House Libra to Scorpio on 12th December 2020. She will remain in Scorpio till January 4, 2021. Even though the transit is very short for the minor planets, the impact is equally important as that of the major planets. After all it requires one day to get a promotion and one day to have an accident. I have analysed the effect of the transit as per the Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>For Aries Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi</strong>: Venus is neutral to the Lagnatipati (Lord of the Ascendant) Mars. Lord of the Second House (House of Wealth, Family) and Lord of the Seventh House (House of Marriage) Venus transiting in the Ashtamasthan (Eighth House - House of Death) brings disputes in matrimonial life. Divorce petitions will be filed. Relations will break. Lovers will become ex-lovers. Family happiness will take a beating. Wealth will be destroyed. Business profits will come down</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>For Taurus Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi</strong>: Venus is the Lagnatipati (Lord of the Ascendant) and hence will give benefits. Lagnatipati (Lord of the Ascendant) in the Seventh house (House of marriage and business) and aspecting the Lagnam (Ascendant) gives happiness in married life. Business profits will zoom. Relations will become intimate between lovers. However, Lord of the Sixth House (House of Health) Venus transiting in the Seventh house (House of marriage and business) makes the spouse sick. Enemies will trouble the business. Profits will come down. Debt will mount.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>For Gemini Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi</strong>: Venus is a thick friend of the Lagnatipati (Lord of the Ascendant) Mercury. Lord of the Twelfth House (House of Losses) Venus transiting in the Sixth House (House of Health) brings enemies, jealousy, debt problems, injuries and accidents. However, Lord of the Fifth House (House of Prosperity) Venus in the Sixth House (House of Health) reduces the prosperity and gives trouble to your children also. Stock market profits will come down</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>For Cancer Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi</strong>: Venus considers the Lagnatipati (Lord of the Ascendant) Moon as enemy. Therefore, benefits will reduce and harm will increase. Lord of the Eleventh House (House of Gains) Venus in the Fifth house (House of prosperity) is good for prosperity, financial gains, friendship, relationship, stock market profits and welfare of the children. Lord of the Fourth House (House of Comforts) Venus transiting in the Fifth house (House of prosperity) brings family comforts, luxuries, properties and vehicles. However, these benefits will be less, as Venus considers the Lagnatipati (Lord of the Ascendant) Moon as enemy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>For Leo Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi</strong>: Lord of the Tenth House (House of Profession) Venus transiting in the Fourth house (House of comforts) brings family comforts, luxuries, properties, vehicles through career and professional benefits. Lord of the Third House (House of Courage and Efforts) Venus in the Fourth house (House of comforts) brings reward for the hard work done and courage shown. Benefits from younger siblings are also on the cards. As Venus and Lagnatipati (Lord of the Ascendant) Sun are enemies, these benefits will be less.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>For Virgo Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi</strong>: Lord of the Ninth House (House of Fortune) Venus in the Third house (House of courage and efforts) brings opportunities and fortunes to be availed through hard work and courage. If you are lazy, you will miss these opportunities and fortunes. Opportunities include foreign trips. Lord of the Second House (House of Wealth, Family) Venus in the Third house (House of courage and efforts) gives wealth but only if you work hard. As Venus is a thick friend of the Lagnatipati (Lord of the Ascendant) Mercury, these benefits will be very stable.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>For Libra Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi</strong>: Ashtamatipati (Lord of the Eighth House) Venus in the Second house (House of wealth and family) destroys wealth and fortunes. However, research scholars will be benefited, and they will get new opportunities abroad. Lagnatipati (Lord of the Ascendant) Venus in the Second house (House of wealth and family) brings wealth for them. It will be a mixed result for them. As Venus is the Lagnatipati (Lord of the Ascendant), benefits will be more and stable. Harm will be less.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>For Scorpio Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi</strong>: Lord of the Seventh House (House of Marriage) Venus in the Lagnam (Ascendant) brings happiness to the married life. Relations will become intimate. Business profits will boom. New ideas will develop in business. However, Lord of the Twelfth House (House of Losses) Venus in the Lagnam (Ascendant) brings heavy losses, health problems, frequent visit to the doctors and increased medical bills. However, relations will flourish. Ex-lovers will be united. Divorce petitions will be withdrawn. As Venus is neutral to the Lagnatipati (Lord of the Ascendant) Mars, there will not be any change in the benefits and harm listed above.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>For Sagittarius Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi</strong>: Lord of the Sixth House (House of Health) Venus in the Twelfth house (House of losses) brings enemies, obstacles, debt problems, diseases, health problems and hospitalization. Relations will also break. Lovers will become ex-lovers. Lord of the Eleventh House (House of Gains) Venus in the Twelfth house (House of losses) wipes out financial gains, friendship and relations. Wishes will not be fulfilled. As Venus is neutral to the Lagnatipati (Lord of the Ascendant) Jupiter, the benefits and harm will remain unchanged.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>For Capricorn Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi</strong>: Lord of the Fifth House (House of Prosperity) Venus transiting in the Eleventh house (House of gains) augurs well for financial gains through other income (non-professional income from other sources like rent, bank interest etc), friendship, relations, fulfillment of wishes, prosperity and benefits to the children. Stock market profits will increase. Lord of the Tenth House (House of Profession) Venus in the Eleventh house (House of gains) will boost up your career/profession. You will get recognition, rewards, increments, promotions and foreign assignments. As Venus and your Lagnatipati (Lord of the Ascendant) Saturn are thick friends, the benefits will multiply.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>For Aquarius Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi</strong>: Lord of the Fourth House (House of Comforts) Venus in the Tenth house (House of profession) gives career boost, family comforts, luxuries, happiness both at home and in office, properties, vehicles etc. Lord of the Ninth House (House of Fortune) Venus in the Tenth house (House of profession) gives you Dharma Karmatipati Yoga (A straightforward person with many fortunes in life and career). As your Lagnatipati (Lord of the Ascendant) Saturn and Venus are thick friends, these benefits will multiply and become stable</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>For Pisces Lagnam (Ascendant) or Rasi</strong>: Lord of the Third House (House of Courage and Efforts) Venus in the Ninth house (House of fortune) makes you search for opportunities and fortunes through your hard work, courage and confidence. With the help of brothers, this could be achieved. Your communication skills could also bring you rewards. Ashtamatipati (Lord of the Eighth House) Venus in the Ninth house (House of fortune) destroys opportunities and fortunes. Spiritualism will take a beating. Mental stress will develop because of many failures. As Venus is neutral to your Lagnatipati (Lord of the Ascendant) Jupiter, the benefits and harm will not change.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Who will gain the most because of the transit? Those who have Capricorn Lagnam (Ascendant) and Rasi and having their natal Venus placed in Scorpio, their Eleventh house (House of gains) will gain a lot with a double Venus effect.&nbsp;Who will be affected adversely by this transit? Those who have Pisces Lagnam (Ascendant) and also Rasi with natal Venus placed in Scorpio will have problems with double Venus.</p>', '0', '2020-12-22 22:44:30.196807', '2020-12-22 22:44:30.196807'),
(47, 831, '#', NULL, '<p>Purva Janma ki Shaap Pida ( Curses of the Past Life) ( Part:1)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With reference to the writings of the Brihad Parashar Hora Shatram, the aadhyay supported &quot; Purvajanma Shaapdyotak Aadhya&quot; covers Serpa Shaap ( Naga Dosha), Pitru Dosha, Anapatya Yoga, Pret Badha, Pishachya Badha and Abhichar Yoga are in very precise and straightforward manner. In this article, I&#39;m trying to illustrate the two most commonly occurring inauspicious yogas out of the above mentioned &nbsp;six well- known inauspicious yogas in jakak&#39;s chart.&nbsp;<br />\r\nFor this, I have drawn the gist of this text from the primary text through the reference of a Marathi book.&nbsp;<br />\r\n1. Serpa-Shaap( Naga-Dosha) : This inauspicious yoga leads to miscarriage in women, or fear Of child death or other problems like delay in child birth which occurs in both charts of males or females. a. It forms when Rahu is placed within the fifth house either in Aries or Scorpio sign. b. This inauspicious yoga also occurs albeit Mars has drusti on Rahu placed in 5th house. c. When Shani making combi with Moon within the house or evenif moon has drusti on Shani placed in 5th house.d. Karak for Child birth is Jupiter, if it&#39;s placed with Rahu in 5th house and Mars in lagna, then also this yoga occurs. e. When malefic Rahu planet is placed in lagna and Mars and Jupiter combo in present in chart and 5th house house lord is present either 6/8/12, then too this bad yoga. For the removal of this bad yoga is Nag pujan with mantra shanti by placing Nag idol made in gold. Donating cow, land, sesame, gold to Brahmin. However the root or the causative planet should be identified by any learned Astrologer then Nagbali pujan is completed to rectify this yoga. One additional but very effective remedy for this is doing fast on Five Panchi ( as per Hindu) tithi for consecutive five Panchmi vrat. In this pujan, &nbsp;five naga idol are made by hand with flour and termeric powder, some milk with water and offering flowers, prasad, rice lahi, then offering this pujan on the very next day in river or any no man&#39;s land under any alone tree.&nbsp;<br />\r\n2 Pisacha Badha/ Pida: a. When malefic planets like Rahu or Ketu are placed in 7th house or Rahu with Moon in lagna and 5th or 9th house occupied with malefic Shani and Mars this inauspicious yoga this is understood to occur. b. In the main chart, the first house when is occupied with Rahu with Shani then also this yoga occurs. In the jatak&#39;s chart, if Ketu occupied with any malefic planet or is seen by malefic planet, then also this yoga is found. c. If natural malefic Shani is placed with malefic/debilitating moon in 8th house this badha is subjected to occur. This yoga worsely results hard suffering life to the jatak. The most effective shanti pujan for the removal of this is Narayan and Nag Bali pujan at the banks of the river with Shiva Temple or Nashik, Ujjain or Gayaji. The auspicious months for this shanti pujan is Shravana/ Bhadrapada/ mahashivratri day/ nagpanchami day/ sankranti/ trayodashi also as panchami tithi of any month out of the 12 months. Remaining yogas are getting to be discussed in my next article. Thanks expecting you feedback eagerly. Composed by Astro Bhushan Ratnakar, Nagpur.</p>', '1', '2020-12-26 10:34:46.746548', '2020-12-26 13:09:28.029430'),
