(58, 8237, '#', NULL, '<p><strong>Sun the king transits to Capricorn on 14th January 2021 :</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The Sun is considered to be soul,father, ancestors, goverenment job and respect to elders. If the Sun is in auspecious position in the chart the native enjoys good career in goverenment jobs and success in political career. If Sun is afflicted or not placed in auspecious places than the native struggles for good career, problems with the seniors in personal and official life. Afflicted sun devoids person from promotions in professional front and the person work is not appreciated.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Sun will be transiting in Capricorn on14thJanuary 2021 the transitof sun from one house to another&nbsp; is known as Sankranti and this transit is known as Makar Sankranti very auspecious for starting new works,jobs and change in climate&nbsp;as Sun rules all the climates. It is observed that after Makar Sankranti climate changes.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Its auspecious to distribute Rice Dals to Poor and needy people on this day. Lot of natives perform Bhandara on this day serving food to poor people.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>As&nbsp; a karminc remedy every one must donate to brahmins on every sankranti this will reduce thenegetive impacts of planets in the native horoscope.</strong></p>', '0', '2021-01-13 18:54:07.838019', '2021-01-13 18:54:07.838019'),
(59, 8237, '#', NULL, '<p><strong>Sun the king transits to Capricorn on 14th January 2021 :</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The Sun is considered to be soul,father, ancestors, goverenment job and respect to elders. If the Sun is in auspecious position in the chart the native enjoys good career in goverenment jobs and success in political career. If Sun is afflicted or not placed in auspecious places than the native struggles for good career, problems with the seniors in personal and official life. Afflicted sun devoids person from promotions in professional front and the person work is not appreciated.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Sun will be transiting in Capricorn on14thJanuary 2021 the transitof sun from one house to another&nbsp; is known as Sankranti and this transit is known as Makar Sankranti very auspecious for starting new works,jobs and change in climate&nbsp;as Sun rules all the climates. It is observed that after Makar Sankranti climate changes.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Its auspecious to distribute Rice Dals to Poor and needy people on this day. Lot of natives perform Bhandara on this day serving food to poor people.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>As&nbsp; a karminc remedy every one must donate to brahmins on every sankranti this will reduce thenegetive impacts of planets in the native horoscope.</strong></p>', '1', '2021-01-13 18:56:23.229446', '2021-01-13 19:48:47.044054'),
(60, 3493, '#', NULL, '<p>सूर्य देव धनु राशि से मकर राशि में 14 जनवरी को सुबह 08.15&nbsp;बजे प्रवेश कर रहे हैं, सूर्य के राशि परिवर्तन को संक्रांति कहा जाता है, सूर्य जब मकर राशि में प्रवेश करते है तो इस राशि परिवर्तन को मकर संक्रांति कहा जाता है, इस वर्ष मकर संक्रांति 14 जनवरी को है।जिसका पुण्य काल सुबह 08.15&nbsp;से साय 04.16 बजे तक है</p>\r\n\r\n<p>मकर संक्रांति शुभ मुहूर्त<br />\r\nपौष माह चल रहा है, मकर संक्रांति पौष मास का प्रमुख पर्व है, इस दिन माघ मास का आरंभ होता है, इस वर्ष मकर संक्रांति पर पूजा पाठ, स्नान और दान के लिए सुबह 8.15&nbsp;बजे से शाम 04.16 तक पुण्य काल रहेगा,</p>', '1', '2021-01-13 20:32:04.418452', '2021-01-13 20:47:44.251226'),
(61, 11557, '#', NULL, '<p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Role of Numerology in our Life</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Numbers are all around us so they have a great impact on our life.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our Date of Birth, Name number, Phone number, Account number, Vehicle number, Flat number and many such things associated with us affect us in a large way.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Some people work so hard... But do not get success but few others who work less hard get good results.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Have you ever thought why?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The possible reason could be wrong vibration of numbers surrounding them with their Date of Birth.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Here is when Numerology comes into play and helps us, guides us in attracting good luck and good fortune by bringing numbers around us in good vibration with us.</p>', '1', '2021-01-13 20:32:15.221171', '2021-01-13 20:45:52.392565'),
(62, 11142, '#', NULL, '<p>मकर संक्रांति के शुभ अवसर पर सूर्य देव की उपासना करने का शुभ समय<br />\r\n08:30 से 10:17 मिनट तक<br />\r\nआपको स्नान करने से पहले गंगाजल और सफेद तिल डालकर पानी में ही स्नान करें<br />\r\nऔर उसके बाद तांबे के कलश में लाल फूल चंदन गुड़ डालकर सूर्य देवता को जल चढ़ाएं</p>', '1', '2021-01-13 21:10:06.335439', '2021-01-14 12:26:56.323859'),
(63, 11158, '#', NULL, '<p>14 जनवरी को मकर संक्रांति का त्योहार मनाया जाएगा। आचार्य अभय मिश्र&nbsp;के मुताबिक,&nbsp;इसका पुण्य काल मुहूर्त सुबह 8.30 से लेकर शाम 5 बजकर 46 मिनट तक रहेगा।&nbsp;वहीं, महापुण्य काल का मुहूर्त सुबह 8.30 से&nbsp;10.15 तक का होगा।&nbsp;स्नान और दान-दक्षिणा जैसे कार्य इस अवधि में किए जा सकते हैं।&nbsp;मकर संक्रांति को महा संक्रांति भी कहा जाता है।</p>\r\n\r\n<p>इस साल की मकर संक्रांति कई मायनों में खास रहने वाली है।&nbsp;मकर संक्रांति के दिन सूर्य उत्तरायण होते&nbsp;है, और मकर राशि में प्रवेश करते&nbsp;है।&nbsp;पौराणिक मान्यताओं के अनुसार, मकर संक्रांति के दिन सूर्य देव अपने पुत्र शनि के घर जाते हैं। मकर संक्रांति से ही ऋतु परिवर्तन भी होने लगता है। ज्योतिष में सूर्य को पिता कहा गया है।&nbsp;सूर्य देव एक साल में 12 राशियों में अलग-अलग समय में भ्रमण करते हैं। और&nbsp;इस राशि परिवर्तन को सूर्य की संक्रांति कहा जाता है।</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>आपका दिन शुभ हो।। धन्यवाद,</p>', '1', '2021-01-13 22:25:48.986296', '2021-01-14 12:26:40.047678'),
(64, 11002, '#', NULL, '<p>Makar Sankranti or Uttarayan celebrates the Sun&#39;s transition into Makar rashi (Capricorn Zodiac sign). On this auspicious day, the Sun comes from the Dakshinayan towards Uttarayan. This position of the Sun is considered as very auspicious. From a religious perspective, on this day, Surya leaves all the issues with his son Shani Dev and comes to meet him at his house (i.e. his Zodiac sign Capricorn). This is why the day of Makar Sankranti is also associated with happiness and prosperity. This day is marked as a favourable meeting of father (Sun) with child (Saturn).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;Like every year, this year also Makar Sankranti 2021 will be celebrated on 14th January throughout the nation with lot of zeal and devotion. But this year there will be conjunction of Sun, Saturn, Jupiter and Mercury in Capricorn sign which will called as stellium. As per Astrology, every native will have different effects based on their ascendant and planets placements in horoscope. Hence proper astrology consultation is required before applying any remedies or rituals. It solely depend on one&rsquo;s chart whether Sun, Saturn or other associated planets are favourable or unfavourable; basis which the donation of substances and other associated rituals can be implemented. Always be mindful, that there could never be general or same remedies for all! For example: say one can donate Til but other cannot depending on Saturn placement in horoscope, same goes with jaggery basis Sun placements in horoscope. Proper Guidance is the Key.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hence consult me before starting with any remedies as if proper solution can make life, incorrect one&rsquo;s can break life.</p>', '0', '2021-01-13 23:12:37.268078', '2021-01-13 23:12:37.268078'),
(65, 11002, '#', NULL, '<p>14 January 2021 is bringing forth a &#39;stellium&#39; which is a conjunction of more than three planets in a sign. It will have Sun, Jupiter, Saturn, and Mercury in one sign of capricorn. Hence its of utmost importance to take guidance and remedies as per your chart..</p>\r\n\r\n<p>May Sun &amp; Saturn GOD bless you all!</p>', '1', '2021-01-13 23:13:08.117512', '2021-01-14 12:14:57.906098'),
(66, 8856, '#', NULL, '<p><strong>Happy Makar Sakranti/Bihu/Pongal to Everyone!!</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The natural Atmakarka(Suryadev) has now entered Capricorn(&#39;Makara&#39;) &amp; will be &#39;Uttarayana&#39;. All auspicious events will now begin be it marriage, Mundan Sanskara, home warming etc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It&#39;s good to chant &#39;Om Shree Suryaya Namah&#39; 108 times on this day by taking a dip in the holy river. One can do the pooja at home also if not possible at a riverside.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hope that the Sungod will bestow his kindness on all of us and wish everyone luck &amp; prosperity! Jai Suryadev!</p>', '1', '2021-01-14 12:20:28.937477', '2021-01-14 12:25:05.301936'),
(67, 7768, '#', NULL, '<p><strong>Wish you Happy Makar Sankranti For all</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Makar Sankranti Translates to &quot;Makar&quot; known as &quot;Capricorn&quot; and &quot;Sankranti&quot; known as &quot;Solistice&quot;. This is the Day, Sun enters into sign of Capricorn in Transit. From this Day the Sun is in North Movement ( Uttarayan).&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>​​​​​​</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '1', '2021-01-14 12:39:47.641222', '2021-01-14 16:18:22.000670'),
(68, 9223, '#', NULL, '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&quot;HAPPY UTTARAYAN TO All&quot;<br />\r\n&nbsp;On the auspicious day of &nbsp;&quot;14th January&quot; &nbsp;a festival celebrated in various parts of country by different names like Makar Sakranti , Lohri , Pongal , Bihu.<br />\r\nSun starts the auspicious Uttarayan movement. People take a dip in holy rivers &nbsp;for &nbsp;attaining Moksha from the endless loop of birth, demise and resurrection. This day Sun enters to Capricorn zodiac sign, &nbsp;which means house of Saturn.&nbsp;<br />\r\nThe relation between Sun and Saturn is of Father and Son. But thier views are opposite and &nbsp;thats why they are knows as enemy.<br />\r\nBut still Sun enters in Saturn house, stays there for almost 30 days and teaches us &nbsp;very important lesson,&nbsp;<br />\r\nto leave your ego, understanding and adjustment between two opposite views of people and live together.<br />\r\nOn this 14th January, 2021 four planets Sun, Mercury, Jupiter and Saturn are together in Capricorn zodiac sign.<br />\r\nThis means Ego, Fighting, difference of opinion, &nbsp;Irritation in relationships.<br />\r\nSo,stay calm, meditate more, pray to God Sun for success and prosperity.<br />\r\nChant below mantras as much as possible 👇<br />\r\n1. &quot;Om Gan Ganpataye &nbsp;namah&quot;<br />\r\n2. &quot;Om Namah Shivay&quot;</p>', '0', '2021-01-15 01:57:46.056080', '2021-01-15 01:57:46.056080'),
(69, 8237, '#', NULL, '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Diseases and Astrology</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our body is composed of five elements viz. Fire,Earth, Air Water and Vayu. For normal health, these elements are in defined proportion called equilibirium. Whenever this equilibrium is disturbed due to excess or deficiency of an element, the health of a person suffers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>When the Element of earth is disturbed it results in causing disease of Flesh, Skin, Joints and hairs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The exited element water brings about disorders in Blood, urine, perspiration, semen and saliva.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Disturbance to the element fire upsets lungs, thirst, sleep and general constitutiojn of the body.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;Disturbance of Air element brings about difficulties in the movements of the limbs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Loss of equilibrium due to ether causes anger, sexuality, fear, and signs of old age.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Element&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Planet&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Sign&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Houses</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fire&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Sun, Mars&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Aries,Leo, Sagitarius&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;1,5,9</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Earth&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Mercury&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Taurus,Virgo,Capricorn&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2,6,10</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Air&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Saturn&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Gemini, Libra,&nbsp; Aquarius&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;3,7, 11</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Water&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Venus, Moon&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Cancer, Scorpion, Pisces&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;4,8,12</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Vayu&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Jupiter,Rahu,Ketu&nbsp; &nbsp;All signs&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; All houses&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Humour Theory</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our body is further composed of three humors called vata (Wind), Pita(Bile) and Kapha(Phlegm).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Planets and Nature of humor they control are:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Humor&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Controlling Planets</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Vata (Wind)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Moon, Mercury ,Venus,Saturn&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Pita (Bile)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Sun, Mars, (Sat,Jupiter, Mercury)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kapha&nbsp; (Phelgm)&nbsp; &nbsp; Jupiter (Moon, Mercury, Venus, Sun)&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nature of disease and parts of body affected will be indicated by the planets and the houses&nbsp; they affect while causing disturbance in any Humor.Planets shown in brackets are secondary planets to cause disease.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6th house in the Natal chart is called the house of general sickness, 8th is ther house of serious sickness , fatasl disease danger and accident. 12th house is the house of self undoing, defect and hospitalization. If&nbsp; Sub-Sub lord of the Ascendant through its Star Lord, links itself with 6th or 8th or 12th Cusap, it indicates that the native is prone to sickness. Simultaneously links with 6 , 8 or 6, 8, 12 are indicative of the fact that he is destined suffer serious sickness, accidents and hospitalization. If the Sub Sub of Ascendant also establishes&nbsp; relations with Markas and Badhakasthana through its Sub or Sub-Sub Lords the disease may ultimately prove Fatal.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '0', '2021-01-15 22:32:43.563157', '2021-01-15 22:32:43.563157'),
