(73, 11002, '#', NULL, '<p><strong>Think before you NAME:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>An earnest advise to all the people, please seek proper guidance in not only coming up with the name of your new born child or reframing your existing name but also your Company or Business name. People put lot of energy, effort, resource, time and hard earned money to run a business, similarly you put your entire life nurturing a child and aspire for them to be successful in respective fields.&nbsp; You or your child and your company can only prosper and reach your dreamt heights, when both the names are in sync and vibrate positively in accordance with your favourable planets and Nakshatra. Ponder over it !</p>', '1', '2021-01-19 13:48:28.516787', '2021-01-19 16:54:28.638333'),
(74, 7768, '#', NULL, '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong>Mental illness in Vedic Astrology</strong><br />\r\nIn Astrologically, what are the combinations one can see if someone is Mentally ill or someone is really going to experience something, that is out of the world or else If someone is temporarily experiencing thing if their Brain does not function Logically.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<strong>The Conditions in Vedic Astrology, Responsible for Mental illness in a Person are</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>The Person 1st and 7th houses in a Birth Chart should be seen.</li>\r\n	<li>If Saturn and Mars are Mutually aspecting each other.</li>\r\n	<li>If the 5th house, which is the house of intelligence, is Placed well or Not.</li>\r\n	<li>The Placement of the Moon. If the Moon is closely conjunct to Sun.</li>\r\n	<li>The Moon is Afflicted with Malefic Planets or not. Placement of the Moon should be seen.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>If a 2 Malefic Planets on either side of Moon, Paap Karti Yoga is Formed. The mind will have a tremendous amount of evil pressure.</li>\r\n	<li>Involvement of the Nodes, Rahu and Ketu, also Functional Malefic Planets ( Functional Malefic Planets are Planets whose Moola Trikona sign is sitting in the 6th, 8th or 12th house) especially 8th or 12th houses. Causes Mental Pressure on the Person.</li>\r\n	<li>When Rahu is closely conjunct with Moon and in the conjunction, if Moon is waning, in the axis of Ketu, at the same time, Functional Malefic Planet aspecting or conjuncting Moon, this is one of the most common things for Mental illness in the Person.</li>\r\n	<li>When Moon is conjuncted to Ketu, or else if Moon with Ketu aspect in 1st, 6th, 8th of 12th houses, the Person is not so much crazy, but so much more axis to the other side of the world. They are Psychic People.</li>\r\n	<li>The Placement of Moon is should be seen. Whether the Moon is Receiving an aspect from Functional Malefics and which house receiving in the Malefic houses 12th, 6th or 8th or 1st or 5th houses. 5th house is the house of intelligence when Moon conjunct the Functional Malefic in the 5th house, they cannot grasp the correct rules in the Society, and there is a chance that these People may turn into Criminals or may do wrong things to others.</li>\r\n</ul>', '0', '2021-01-19 15:00:07.464927', '2021-01-19 15:00:07.464927'),
(75, 11071, '#', NULL, '<p><strong>Importance of match making in marriage&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>One should take care of kundli Milan (Matchmaking) before marriage. Because our nature and karma is dependent upon planets. In a &nbsp;nutshell our total life is dependent on planets.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In matchmaking one must check manglik dosha. If Mars is in lagna(Ascendent) 4th house 7th house 8th house and 12th house of boy or girl gives manglik dosha.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>lagna&nbsp; is self and 7th house is of marriage. If fiery Mars is placed in these houses. It will burn the karkatwa. 1st house is 7th from 7th. Which is also house of love and attraction . 8th house is 2nd from 7th growth of partnership is known as maraksthan. Mars here can spoil the married life. 12th house is 6th from 7th house in counting. Which is house of obstacles, disease and&nbsp; enmity. Mars here also gives trouble in marriage life.&nbsp; Similarly 4th house is 10th house (karamsthan)&nbsp; of 7th house. Mars placed in this house will destroy it&#39;s karkatwa.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6th house is 12th from 7th house which is house&nbsp; of loss of marriage so Mars placed in this house may give bad result.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong>Upaay(remedies)</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>1.If both boy and girl are manglik then this dosh get cancelled.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2.If Jupiter is strong in girl&rsquo;s horoscope and Venus is strong in boys&rsquo; horoscope and Mars is in debilitation in above said houses&nbsp; then marriage may happen.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3.Boy and girl rashi &nbsp;should be of &nbsp;friendly sign and should match more than 27 gunas then manglik Dosha&nbsp; gets weak .</p>', '1', '2021-01-19 19:28:39.112662', '2021-01-20 14:05:10.543430'),
(76, 8407, '#', NULL, '<p>Venus in 12th house- Venus in 12th house may give hidden love and that may not be long lasting one. People with Venus in 12th house may not give good understanding in relationship. Marrriage for people with 12th house may give long delays. Venus in 12th house may give more interest towards bed comforts and sensual pleasures. People with Venus in 12th house may be more emotional and sensitive.&nbsp;</p>', '1', '2021-01-20 14:05:57.588635', '2021-01-21 10:42:39.098022'),
(77, 831, '#', NULL, '<p>What is a Nadi Dosha?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nadi is one of the eight gunas that are used to calculate compatibility with your partner. A total of 36 points are there out of which Nadi has maximum points i.e. 8. Now if there is any conflict between the Nadi of two persons; then they have to suffer from Nadi dosha.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If there is no middle Nadi Dosha in the horoscope of the bride and groom. The eight dots that occur during property matching are also called Koot or Ashtakoot. These eight codes are varna, vasya, tara, vagina, planetary friendship, gana, bhakuta, and Nadi. There are three types of Nadi &ndash; Arya Nadi, Madhya Nadi, and Antya Nadi. Each person&rsquo;s birth chart shows the presence of the moon in a particular constellation of that person&rsquo;s pulse. Out of the total 27 Nakshatras, nine special constellations have one of the Nadi of the native due to the presence of the Moon.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Acharya Bhushan</p>', '0', '2021-01-21 11:05:34.898953', '2021-01-21 11:05:34.898953'),
(78, 831, '#', NULL, '<p>Cancellation of Naadi Dosha in Match-Making:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>During Match making of a bride and groom, Nadi, as per the Ashatkoot Milan System&nbsp;carries 8 points.If this guna is not matching then it is considered as a Mahadosha (Major defect) like infertility for child, health issues in both persons after marriage, uncompatibility of all kinds ( physical and mental). However,&nbsp;the dosha caused due to its mismatch is considered cancelled if one or more of the following conditions are satisfied.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(1) Both have same Rashi but different constellations.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(2) Both have same constellation but different Rashi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(3) Both have same birth constellation but different Charans (parts).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Acharya Bhushan Ratnakar</p>', '0', '2021-01-21 11:10:53.653388', '2021-01-21 11:10:53.653388'),
(79, 8407, '#', NULL, '<p>Sunapha yoga- This yoga is auspcious caused by benefic planets like Jupiter and Venus placed in 2nd house from the Moon.&nbsp; Natives with this yoga will rise to high positions in life due to their self efforts. This yoga may bring luck and fame with high values. Natives will be able to gain satisfaction with their hard work and especially this may happen during the mahadasa of planets which is giving Sunapha yoga</p>', '1', '2021-01-21 11:26:30.470440', '2021-01-21 14:15:05.746633'),
(80, 8237, '#', NULL, '<p><em><strong>Shashtamsha D-6 Chart for diseases.</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>This chart is seen for proneness to physical illness and its cure. The attitude or anxiety in the profession, debts, litigations, disputes and enemies are also seen from this varga. The general health is studied.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>1--&gt;6th lord in the birth chart is the main significator in D6 chart. When this afflicted 6th lord is placed in lagna of D6, it denotes problems. The problems are visible in the dasha of most malefic planet.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>2--&gt; Mars even in 6th house of D6 is good and stops illness. The placement of Mars with respect to 6th lord of birth chart is seen in D6. If it is 3/11 or 4/10 then good and stops illness. Association of Mars with 6th,8th,12th, 2nd house /lordsd gives no resistence to disease.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>3--&gt; 6th house is 11th to 8th house. A strong 6th house contribute strength to 8th. It gives longivity and disease free life.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>4--&gt; Relation of Lagna lord od D1, Lagna lord of D3 and Ketu is seen in D6 for cure.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>5--&gt;Ketu is the significator of illness. The relation of Ketu with 6th lord of natal chart is seen in D6. When they are badly placed from each other then we can expect trouble from illness.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>6--&gt; When 6th lord of birth chart is afflicted by Rahu , Ketu or Saturn in D8, the person suffers crippling disease like cancer etc.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>7--&gt; The 8th lord of the birth chart when similarly afflicted by Rahu, Ketu or Saturn, gives serious physical accident.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Remedies mus be performed in advance to get rid of diseases.</strong></p>', '1', '2021-01-21 16:04:26.768153', '2021-01-21 17:01:21.420892'),
(81, 831, '#', NULL, '<p>What is Nadi Dosha?&nbsp;<br />\r\nNadi is one of the eight Gunas that are used to calculate compatibility with your partner. There are a total of 36 points, of which Nadi has maximum points (8 out of 36 gunnas). Now when there is a conflict between two people&#39;s nadi ; then they must suffer from nadi dosha.<br />\r\nIf there is no middle nadi dosha in the horoscope of the bride and groom. The eight points that occur during property matching are also known as koot or ashtakoot. These eight codes are Varna, Vasya, Tara, Vagina, Planetary Friendship, Gana, Bhakuta, and Nadi.<br />\r\n&nbsp;There are three types of Nadi: Adya Nadi, Madhya Nadi, and Antya Nadi. Each person&#39;s birth card shows the presence of the moon in a particular constellation of that person. Of the 27 nakshatras, nine particular constellations have one of the nadi of the natives due to the presence of the moon.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Regards</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Acharya Bhushan Ratnakar</p>', '0', '2021-01-28 15:37:25.804603', '2021-01-28 16:46:27.790547'),
(82, 831, '#', NULL, '<p>Rejection of Nadi Dosha during Match Making</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Eight points are awarded for match-making by a bride and groom, Nadi, according to the Ashtakoot Milan system under Vedic Jyotish. If this guna does not fit, it is considered a mahadasha (serious defect) as infertility in children, health problems in both persons after marriage, intolerances of all kinds (physical and mental). Hence, the Dosha caused due to its mismatch is deemed to be canceled if one or more of the following conditions are met:&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;(1) Both have the same conditions as Rashi, but different constellations.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;(2) Both have the same constellation but different Rashi.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;(3) Both have the same birth constellation, but different charans (parts).&nbsp;<br />\r\nAcharya Bhushan Ratnakar</p>', '1', '2021-01-28 15:37:52.325961', '2021-01-28 16:35:20.051311'),
(83, 3493, '#', NULL, '<p>माघ मास के कृष्ण पक्ष की चतुर्थी तिथि को संकष्टी चतुर्थी या सकट &nbsp;चौथ रूप में मनाया जाता है, इस दिन विशेष रूप से गणेश जी की पूजा का महत्त्व होता है। पौराणिक कथाओं के अनुसार इसी दिन भगवान् शिव ने गणेश जी का शीश काटने के बाद उन्हें गजशीश लगाकर पुनर्जीवित किया था और गजानन के रूप में गणेश जी का पुनर्जीवन आरम्भ हुआ तभी से इस दिन को संकष्टी चतर्थी के रूप में मनाया जाता है और भगवान &nbsp;गणेश जी की विशेष पूजा अर्चना की जाती है ऐसी मान्यता है के ये दिन सभी संकटो का हरण करने वाला होता है इसलिए ये संकट चौथ या सकट चौथ के नाम से भी प्रसिद्ध है। सकट चौथ के व्रत में चंद्र दर्शन का विशेष महत्त्व होता है और इस बार चंद्रोदय के समय चतुर्थी तिथि 31 जनवरी को ही उपस्थित रहेगी इसलिए &nbsp;इस बार 31 जनवरी रविवार के दिन सकट चौथ का व्रत किया जायेगा।</p>', '1', '2021-01-30 10:32:04.071663', '2021-01-30 10:37:26.416828'),
(84, 8237, '#', NULL, '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Siddhamsa D-24 Chart for Education /higher education</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The 12th house is the immediateTpast and hence the dwadasamsa represents the people who are our immidiate predessors or elders like father,mother and grandparents. The Siddhamsa (D-24 Chart) is the higher&nbsp; harmonic of this chart in the plane of mental conciousness and indicates the learning process.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Important houses and Karkas::</p>\r\n\r\n<p>a) 4th Formal Education:Mercury,Moon</p>\r\n\r\n<p>b) 5th ; Knowledge :&nbsp; Jupiter&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>c) 9th ; Higher Education : Jupiter, Sun</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Milestones in Education Career::</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We know that 4th is the house of formal learning or schooling, where the child learns ways of the world, 9th is the house of advanced studies, where the child attains the knowledge of the teacher and capable of guiding others. It is well known that 9th is the house of higher education and shows graduation in any discipline. Note that the 9th house is 6th from&nbsp; 4th house indicating a marked change or growth(6th is an Upachaya or house of growth). Thus, by completing formal school education and going to college the native has grown. Extending the same principle, we can say that 6th house from 9th , i.e., the 2nd&nbsp; house shall represents further education or the masters degree and then the 7th house (6th from 2nd house) will represents even further education such as doctorate or so.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The Sun and Moon in Siddhamsa</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Moon :: Moon, is the Karka of mind. Whether a person will have fixity of mind in studies is seen from the Moon in Siddhamsa. If the Moon is placed in Fixed(Sthira) Siddhamsa, the native has stability of mind and has concentrated, focused mind while studying.However the moon is placed in movable sign, the native will have difficulties in pursuing his studies with full concentration.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Dispositor of Moon if well placed and associate with the Lagna through aspect of conjunction gives good analytical skills and prepares the stage for a good scholar.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sun:: The placement of Sun shall indicate, where the knowledge would come from., e.g. if Sun is placed in 9th house, then this could be from higher education. If Rahu anyway influences him, then there are chances of native gaining knowledge from foreign countries or his studies influenced by foreign culture.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Influence of various planets on the subject of education::</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Jupiter joining/aspecting the above planets in the 1st/5th will give all around knowledge, both traditional and modern and profiency in atleast one branch.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Mercury :</strong>: Karkatva is communication and speech and hence it governs Communication through electronic journalism,media etc. This is why Mercury also governs Mantras and astrology. Saturn :: Saturn is a great teacher.It teaches through punishment and making one realise the purpose of Life. Hence it signifies philosophy and spirtualism. Saturn signifies the knowledge of creation. When coupled with Jupiter it generates fruitful Brahma Yoga which grants the fine knowledge of creation and also shows passing down of knowledge from tradition through a Guru (Jupiter)&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Venus :: Venus rules the real world and hence signify the knowledge of private sector and rules the operation level management skills. The combination of Moon Venus can signify sailing or navigation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mars:: The ability governed by Mars is that of logical and analytical reasoning . Being a fiery planet, Mars can also give knowledge of Jyotisha. when it joins Jupiter</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ketu :: Ketu gives the knowledge of Mathematics, Statistics and astrology</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Rahu:: Rahu signifies studies or knowledge on Imports etcc..</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Disruptors/ Badhakas/Markas ::</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3rd house :: 3rd house is 12th from 4th house of formal education, hence 3rd lord can disrupt education, when it aspects the dasa rasi or associate with in any other way.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>10th house :: The 10th house is second (Marka) for the 9th house and indicates termination of education and the beginning of career /profession.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '1', '2021-02-02 17:15:27.225564', '2021-02-03 15:25:45.928671'),
(85, 7768, '#', NULL, '<p><strong>Ketu Mahadasha in Vedic Astrology</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Ketu is the South Node of Moon. Ketu Dasha is 7 years long.</li>\r\n	<li>Ketu Planet is meant for letting go of things, letting go of the Material world and embracing the spiritual world.</li>\r\n	<li>Ketu is the Planet shows that we have already accomplished in Past life and we don&#39;t care to concentrate on them as much in this life.</li>\r\n	<li>Ketu is a Spiritual Planet.</li>\r\n	<li>In Ketu Mahadasha, Majority of People may lose wealth on their own or without their consent.</li>\r\n	<li>In Ketu Mahadasha, People really feel that they want to discover themselves.</li>\r\n	<li>For some People in Ketu Mahadasha, Ketu gives more than it takes.</li>\r\n	<li>Majority of the time, Ketu teaches about the difference between Temporary things and Permanent things.</li>\r\n	<li>Remedy to get success in Ketu Mahadasha,&nbsp;Person need not be run for material things, the more the Person run for Material things, Ketu may take away. A person has to be Spiritual in his or her Ketu Mahadasha.</li>\r\n	<li>Ketu Mahadasha is favourable when Ketu is in 2nd or in 11th houses. Ketu gives a lot of gains and wealth.</li>\r\n	<li>Generally, Ketu works well in Aries, Cancer, Leo, Scorpio, Sagittarius and Pisces sign.</li>\r\n	<li>First, check the sign of Ketu in which sign it is placed. Ketu is a shadow planet, Works as sign lord and nakshatra lord in its dasha. Then, check the sign lord and Nakshatra lord of Ketu planet. How it is Placed. If sign lord and Nakshatra lord are placed well, you get good results. If not you may face bad results.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Example:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>In Ketu Mahadasha, if Ketu is in 8th house. A person has to be careful regarding Journeys, there is a chance of accidents or injuries.</li>\r\n	<li>If Ketu is in 6th house and does not Place well, in Ketu Mahadasha, Person has to be careful regarding health and habits. Health may be spoiled and Person may be hospitalised.</li>\r\n	<li>So a person has to be careful in his or her Ketu Mahadasha, Especially if they have weak Ketu.</li>\r\n</ul>', '1', '2021-02-05 09:06:32.306252', '2021-02-05 11:20:59.300722'),
(86, 3493, '#', NULL, '<p>आने वाली 9 तारिख को एक बड़ा ही दुर्लभ संयोग बनने वाला है जो सामान्यतः देखने को नहीं मिलता, वर्तमान ग्रहस्थिति को देखें तो मकर राशि में शनि और बृहस्पति का संचार तो काफी लम्बे समय से चल रहा है पर पिछले माह सूर्य और शुक्र का प्रवेश भी मकर राशि में होने से मकर राशि में चतुर्ग्रही योग तो बना हुआ है पर अब 5 फरवरी को वक्री बुध का भी प्रवेश हो जायेगा और इसके बाद विशेष रूप से 9 फरवरी की रात को 8 बजकर 31 मिनट&nbsp;पर चन्द्रमाँ भी मकर राशि में प्रवेश कर जायेगा जिसके बाद मकर राशि में एक साथ 6 ग्रह (शनि बृहस्पति सूर्य शुक्र बुध और चन्द्रमाँ) उपस्थित होंगे और मकर राशि में &quot;षड-ग्रह योग&quot; बन जायेगा जो ज्योतिष की दृष्टि से एक बहुत दुर्लभ संयोग है जो कई वर्षों में एक बार बनता है और इसके अलग अलग अच्छे बुरे परिणाम भी होते हैं। इस बार ये &quot;षड-ग्रह योग&quot; 9 फरवरी की रात 8:31 से शुरू होकर 11 फरवरी की पूरी रात तक उपस्थित रहेगा।</p>', '1', '2021-02-06 09:05:45.197870', '2021-02-06 14:25:47.528854'),
(87, 8237, '#', NULL, '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Combination of Mars, Venus and Rahu&nbsp; False promises of marriage and seperation</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The Combination results in extreme sexual indulgence and false promises of marriage.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>If the combination is in a girl&rsquo;s horoscope, she will start going through all kinds of physical enjoyment at a very tender age. She develops sexual relations with the person she lovesand would regard him as her husband. Unfortunately it has generally been observed in many cases that the boy and the girl fail to marry despite having relations with each other for years together. The marriage does not take due to infatuation among boy and girl. Rahu separates them. Sun and Saturn and Rahu have separative tendencies where as Mars and Venus attract each other and create passion, lust and adultery. Mars and Venus are extremely sensual. This combination has special reference to the ascendants ruled by Mars and Venus i.e. Aries, Taurus, Libra and Scorpio. One makes contacts with a number and obviously marital life and conjugal happiness suffer.</strong></p>', '0', '2021-02-18 12:07:02.377059', '2021-02-18 12:07:02.377059'),
