(98, 7768, '#', NULL, '<p><br />\r\n<strong>Mental illness in Vedic Astrology</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>In Astrologically, what are the combinations one can see if someone is Mentally ill or someone is really going to experience something, that is out of the world or else If someone is temporarily experiencing thing if their Brain does not function Logically.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The conditions in Vedic Astrology, Responsible for Mental illness in a Person</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>The Person 1st and 7th houses in a Birth Chart should be seen.</li>\r\n	<li>If Saturn and Mars are Mutually aspecting each other.</li>\r\n	<li>If the 5th house, which is the house of intelligence, is Placed well or Not.</li>\r\n	<li>The Placement of the Moon. If the Moon is closely conjunct to Sun.</li>\r\n	<li>The Moon is Afflicted with Malefic Planets or not. Placement of the Moon should be seen.</li>\r\n	<li>If a 2 Malefic Planets on either side of Moon, Paap Karti Yoga is Formed. The mind will have a tremendous amount of evil pressure.</li>\r\n	<li>Involvement of the Nodes, Rahu and Ketu, also Functional Malefic Planets ( Functional Malefic Planets are Planets whose Moola Trikona sign is sitting in the 6th, 8th or 12th house) especially 8th or 12th houses. Causes Mental Pressure on the Person.</li>\r\n	<li>When Rahu is closely conjunct with Moon and in the conjunction, if Moon is waning, in the axis of Ketu, at the same time, Functional Malefic Planet aspecting or conjuncting Moon, this is one of the most common things for Mental illness in the Person.</li>\r\n	<li>When Moon is conjuncted to Ketu, or else if Moon with Ketu aspect in 1st, 6th, 8th of 12th houses, the Person is not so much crazy, but so much more axis to the other side of the world. They are Psychic People.</li>\r\n	<li>The Placement of Moon is should be seen. Whether the Moon is Receiving an aspect from Functional Malefics and which house receiving in the Malefic houses 12th, 6th or 8th or 1st or 5th houses. 5th house is the house of intelligence when Moon conjunct the Functional Malefic in the 5th house, they cannot grasp the correct rules in the Society, and there is a chance that these People may turn into Criminals or may do wrong things to others.</li>\r\n</ul>', '0', '2021-03-12 13:28:53.457728', '2021-03-12 13:28:53.457728'),
(99, 7768, '#', NULL, '<p><strong>Mars Mahadasha in Vedic Astrology</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Mars Represents Brother, Will Power, Drive to accomplish something, Fighting ability, Anger, Mars represents injuries, Surgeries, Accidents, Blood Disorders, Fever. Mars represents your Sex drive.</li>\r\n	<li>During Mars Mahadasha, the Person drive, with the power to succeed or accomplish a goal increases.</li>\r\n	<li>When Mars Mahadasha comes, the Person whatever they want to do, they do it.</li>\r\n	<li>During Mars Mahadasha, whatever house it is ruling those houses are activated. And wherever it placed that also activated. These become important.</li>\r\n	<li>If Mars is ruling the 2nd or 11th house, the Person gets wealth and assets, During Mars Mahadasha.</li>\r\n	<li>During Mars Dasha, when Mars in the 1st, 4th, 10th house and well placed, the Person inclines towards the Real estate.</li>\r\n	<li>If Mars is well Placed, in Mars Dasha the person gets Property, Mars is a significator of Land, Home and Real estate Business.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>If Mars is Badly Placed in Horoscope</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>When Mars is debilitated, it makes a Person very clever, it makes a person how to take action and do something, he can gain.</li>\r\n	<li>If Mars is weak if it is with Malefic Planets, or If Mars in Dustana Places ( 6th, 8th or 12th house)</li>\r\n	<li>The Person may get an injury that leads to surgery.</li>\r\n	<li>Accidents may happen to the Person.</li>\r\n	<li>Mars also represents fear in a Person, so when Mars is strong, in good dignity, it gives will power to face anything. If Mars is not in good dignity, Fear comes to a Person.</li>\r\n	<li>The Person gets into a lot of Arguments and Fights.</li>\r\n	<li>Also, may create disharmony between the person Male Friends, and with Brothers. Family Disputes may happen.</li>\r\n</ul>', '0', '2021-03-13 07:31:43.686991', '2021-03-13 07:31:43.686991'),
