orship of Maa Bhagwati every morning (if possible before 12:00 pm) and in the evening (6 pm to 10 pm). There are different ways for worshiping but the chanting of Durga Shaptashati either in Hindi, English or in Sanskrit is the best.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; In Durga Saptashati there are different mantra&rsquo;s for solving different problems in life.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Everyone should do proper worship (the kalash sathapana, Saptashati path, and on last day by offering gifts and food to girl child) of Maa Bhagwati in Navratri at least once in life.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>7.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Maa Bhagwati path can fulfill all the wish of person. In this year the Chitra Navratri has started from 13 April and will end on 21st April.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You should follow these remedies from today</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Shardiya Navratri will start from 7 October to 15th October 2021.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Jai Mata Di..God Bless to all of you...</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '0', '2021-04-18 06:27:57.698640', '2021-04-18 06:27:57.698640'),
