(123, 8237, '#', NULL, '<p>&nbsp;↩ Mars Retrograde in 7th house --- Arguing more with your partner &hearts;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you have Mars retro in 7th house, you may be arguing more with your partner. Re-assess how to handle conflict with one another. If you are not pushing hard yourself enough in your relationship, try to understand what is holding you back from affirming your position. Then persuade your partner that you mean what you say. &hearts; But gently. &hearts; If you are too hard to your partner, too demanding, then step it back a notch. Or several Notches.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>🎵Anurag Saxena 🎵</p>', '1', '2021-05-14 23:15:12.445988', '2021-05-15 10:26:29.882341'),
(124, 1679, '#', NULL, '<p>Akshaya tritya is the third lunar day of vaihsakh month and this is the Special day becouse The Sun and Moon both exalted on that day and make this day special in many way. while our ancestors used to do an act of generous, kind, and gave gift(daan) to needful people of society as we see that The two lunar god exalted same time only once a year while the lord Sun is a great example of doing work for others as the incarnation of lord Ram (who is the avtar of the Sun)&nbsp; spent whole life for the benifit of society while the Karna ( lord Sun son) who was a great philianthropist (daanvir). while krishna ( the moon incarnation) also did lot of leela for soceity well beings.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>there is a temple in vrindavan where the lotus feet of lord krishna displayed at the temple only on Akshaya Tritya day. all devotee of Krishna should visit it and it will work wonder for those in whose chart The Sun or Moon were diblitated or eclipsed or weaken while also boost those who have good placement of these.</p>', '1', '2021-05-15 11:32:35.670546', '2021-05-15 12:58:44.547389'),
(125, 13293, '#', NULL, '<p>Role of Numerology in our life...&nbsp;<br />\r\nNumbers are all around us so they have a great impact on our life.<br />\r\nOur Date of Birth, Name number, Phone number, Account number, Veichle number, Flat number and many such things associated with us affect us in a large way.<br />\r\nSome people work so hard... But do not get success but few others who work less hard get good results.<br />\r\nHave you ever thought why?<br />\r\nThe possible reason could be wrong vibration of numbers surrounding them with their Date of Birth.<br />\r\nHere is when Numerology comes into play and helps us, guides us in attracting good luck and good fortune by bringing numbers around us in good vibration with us.</p>', '0', '2021-05-17 00:24:50.362914', '2021-05-17 00:24:50.362914'),
(126, 15122, '#', NULL, '<p><strong>WHY CHOOSE TAROT?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>What is Tarot?</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>In layman terms, Tarot is a tool to connect with your intuition which guides you to choose the correct path.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>What readings we can get from Tarot? </strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Well to be precise we can get answers to straight forward yes/no questions. If we want to know timing of some event then Tarot is the way to get the information. It can also give you insight into your past, present and future.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Many times in life we come across a situation where we are at a crossroads and unable to decide which way to go.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Lets suppose you got offer from more than one company and all the offers you have are equally good, then in this situation Tarot helps to guide you which company you should choose.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In relationship issues, it can guide what is the current situation and how to make that relationship better.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tarot can help identify things causing obstacles in life and guides you to resolve that situation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It can also guides you about your health whether you are on right track of improving it or not.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Apart from all this, it also unfolds whole Birth Chart for you without even your birth details.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>You must be thinking, what is the validity of Tarot Reading? </strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Tarot is all about energies and our Karma. Our decisions and actions create our Karma. So when we take some action, then our Karma changes accordingly and hence our future.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>That is why one never should ask repeated questions from tarot otherwise it will start giving confusing answers. A person can ask again after few months or when that event already happened, because at that time our energies already changed.</p>', '1', '2021-05-17 21:16:47.268540', '2021-05-18 11:00:06.858354'),
(127, 8237, '#', NULL, '<p><strong>♐ </strong>Jupiter transit to Shatabhisha Nakshatra from 22nd May 2021 to 20 July First round (Some relief from Covid) <strong>🎭</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; <strong>♨</strong><strong> Aspect</strong> &nbsp;on Bharani, Punarvasu and Poorvaphalguni Nakshatra <strong>♨</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Jupiter will be traveling to Shatbhisha Nakshatra from 22nd May 2021 in the lord of this Nakshatra is Rahu. Jupiter will be aspecting to 3 Nakshatras namely Bharani, Punarvasu and Poorvaphalguni this is a good aspect as the positive energies will be received by Nakshatras ruled by Venus, Jupiter and Rahu. Jupiter will remain in direct motion till 19th June 2021 after that it will be in retrograde motion in Shatbhisha Nakshatra. The suffering of Covid will be reduced during this period due to positive energies of Jupiter to the Nakshatras. The natives with these Nakshatras will be benefitted by income generation sources, new employments and health recoveries.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If these Nakshatras are afflicted (Bharani, Punarvasu, Poorvaphalguni) in the natal chart, they will be benefited by Jupiter aspects. On the other hand Rahu based Nakshatras (Ardra, Swati, and Shatabhisha) may also get positive energies of Jupiter. Pandemic will reduce to a lower level during this period.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Benefit to the Nakshatras</strong>:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>🔺</strong> Bharani, Punarvasu, Poorvaphalguni, Ardra, Swati, Shatbhisha. <strong>🔺</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>🎵 </strong>Anurag Saxena <strong>🎵</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '0', '2021-05-18 18:03:22.209624', '2021-05-18 18:03:22.209624'),
