(157, 16540, '#', NULL, '<p>💯💯 Aries<br />\r\nLove relations between you two will improve and you&rsquo;ll spend quality time with your beloved.<br />\r\nOverall, this transit is bringing mixed results for Aries natives.<br />\r\n💯💯 Taurus<br />\r\nyou&rsquo;re likely to earn good. Your sources of income can increase and you may earn profit from matters related to property and real estate.<br />\r\n💯💯 Gemini<br />\r\nOn one hand, there can be tiffs with your partner, while on the other, ideological differences can arise between you and your spouse. This transit will be least favourable for Gemini natives.<br />\r\n💯💯 Cancer<br />\r\nYou can gain mixed results in several matters during this time. In case you&rsquo;re married, then Cancer natives must look after their spouse&rsquo;s health.<br />\r\n💯💯 Leo<br />\r\nSimilarly, communicate openly but nicely with your spouse in order to avoid any argument and maintain a warm relationship with him/her. Children in the family may act stubbornly.<br />\r\n💯💯 Virgo<br />\r\nYou&rsquo;ll gain profits in your business and there is a possibility of you getting a promotion in your workspace.<br />\r\n💯💯 Libra<br />\r\nyour financial conditions will improve. Due to the favourable effects of Sun, you may witness tremendous benefits within your workspace.<br />\r\n💯💯 Scorpio<br />\r\nAs a result, you must look after yourself, eat healthy and exercise daily. But with constant efforts, you&rsquo;ll be able to achieve your objective.<br />\r\n💯💯 Sagittarius<br />\r\nYou may come across sudden gains, and this transit will prove to be moderately favorable for you.<br />\r\n💯💯 Capricorn<br />\r\nThere is a possibility of judgement being ruled in your favour in case you&rsquo;re dealing with a court case. Hence, give your 100% and do not take a step back.<br />\r\n💯💯 Aquarius<br />\r\nKeeping the aspect of health aside, this transit of Sun can prove to be fruitful for Aquarians.<br />\r\n💯💯Pisces<br />\r\nThere can be disputable situations arising within the family, which will become the cause of stress and tension.</p>', '0', '2021-06-15 13:02:50.098421', '2021-06-15 13:02:50.098421'),
