(218, 18, '#', NULL, '<p>Astrology core lies in the law of karma. We are the sum of innumerable lifetimes. The experience of these innumerable lifetimes manifests in the form of our personality and the life situations we are going to attract.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We can understand it like every person when born comes with their software program which is constantly expanded and modified in each lifetime and form the basis of our thought process and life struggles.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our soul is just part of God which has become impure due to various external influences. Once we purify our soul we will again immense in the infinite energy of God. These innumerable lifetimes are struggles for purifying ourselves. It is like we are in a school where we have to pass the exams. Once you pass the exam of the highest class you will eventually merge in the pure energy of God.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Now consider each lifetime as a class where you have to learn certain lessons and pass the exam. The difference is that you don&rsquo;t have a syllabus and you don&rsquo;t even know what you have to learn. In this class, all the tests which happen are surprise tests. Some are comparably easy and others tough but are sure to happen. If we don&rsquo;t pass the exam of this lifetime class then we have to come again and send one more lifetime for learning the same lessons and give similar tests.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Now, here comes free will. What and how much we learn and grow in this lifetime is our own hands. If we learn our lesson consciously then tests will still appear periodically but it will be easy for us to clear it.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I am quoting lines of Yogananda from his book &lsquo;Autobiography of a Yogi &lsquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;A child is born on that day and at that hour when the celestial rays are in mathematical harmony with his individual karma. His Horoscope is a challenging portrait, revealing his unalterable past and its probable future results. But the natal chart can be rightly interpreted only by men of intuitive wisdom. Occasionally, I told astrologers to select my worst periods, according to planetary indications, and I would still accomplish whatever task set for myself. It is true that my success at such times has been accompanied by extraordinary difficulties but faith in divine protection and conscious effort from one&rsquo;s side are forces formidable beyond any other&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our birth chart clearly indicates the area where we have to learn lessons. If we learn those lessons beforehand through spiritual practices or behavioural patterns, we might attract less intensity of events because our learning is already complete.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Astrology should be utilized to guide one with ways to deal with karma and ultimately rising above it, Like in the case of a storm, all the birds seek shelter but eagles avoid the storm by flying above it. Similarly, we can make ourselves capable to rise above the storms of life.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As Long as we take birth in physical form, the law of karma will affect us in one way or another and it would be useful if we could achieve an understanding of the karmic pattern to be deal with in this lifetime if no other reason than that it would enable us to face our destiny with grace and acceptance and will not come as a surprise.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '1', '2021-08-06 20:20:11.996796', '2021-08-08 11:45:56.427786'),
(219, 831, '#', NULL, '<p>For the removal of Inauspicious Rahu effects ( Rahu in the Dhanu/Mesha/Karka/Singh/Vrushchika/Meena Rashi) in the birth chart&nbsp;or his Mahadasha if going&nbsp;on. Native needs to please Rahu by chanting the Mantra Om Ram Rahve namh or Om Bhram Brim Bhrim Bhrom Sah Rahve namh for 108 times in the Morning and evening. Worshiop lord Shiva and lord Kal Bhairava daily. Keeping one Silver Goli (ball of 4-5 grams in pocket or purse). Offering 4-&nbsp;mooli to lord&nbsp; Shiva or to&nbsp;Bhrahmin on Saturday Morning after placing it over the head or pillow at Friday Night. Shubham Bhavatu</p>', '1', '2021-08-11 13:00:26.909639', '2021-08-11 13:57:30.063407'),
(220, 18865, '#', NULL, '<p>Heart related issues:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you are suffering from any heart related issues or get upset with small happenings even that means your sun is weak. To improve it chant gayatri mantra 108 times with rudraksha mala on Sunday during sunrise.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It will improve your sun as well as help in heart related disorders</p>', '1', '2021-08-12 10:08:18.479775', '2021-08-13 17:21:57.425827'),
(221, 18865, '#', NULL, '<p>Remove stale flowers from your temple</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Keeping stale flowers in temple upsets maa lakshmi as she considers it as a disrespect.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>So discard the flowers next day of worship and also remove broken things from home to make maa lakshmi happy</p>', '1', '2021-08-12 10:10:46.133690', '2021-08-13 18:06:59.729857'),
(222, 18865, '#', NULL, '<p>Hanuman kavach:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Offer sindhiir and chameli oil to hanuman ji on tuesday, bring some sindhoor back home and write &quot;om&quot; With it on your vehicle, it acts as a kavach and prevents from accidents.&nbsp;</p>', '1', '2021-08-16 20:53:06.591582', '2021-08-18 10:18:29.024100'),
(223, 18865, '#', NULL, '<p>To remove obstacles in education:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you are facing obstacles in education field, donate some study material to poor children atleast 2-3 times a year on Thursday. It will help removing the obstacles along with your hard work</p>', '1', '2021-08-16 20:55:09.002448', '2021-08-18 10:19:17.305882'),
(224, 3745, '#', NULL, '<p>What are Tarot cards?&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tarot comes from the river taro, where the popular Game of tarocchi, was played in early 15th century.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It was not designed as a tool of devination, it became popular as a fortune telling aid in the late 18th century. From 18th century to present day Tarots have evolved far beyond being a tool for fortune telling.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Aside from divination, Tarot cards are used for mediatation, mind mapping and spiritual and personal guidance. People from all walks of life are turning to tarot for guidance in decision making.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>These cards are made with different pictures with bright which carry significant meaning.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>These card help a person to understand what he or she needs to do in a particular situation as reading give a person insight to past, current and future events. Based on a person&#39;s current path at the time of reading.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is important to stress that everyone has free will and choice to make their own decision. The cards are for guidance but our destiny is ours alone.&nbsp;</p>', '0', '2021-08-19 18:45:45.310936', '2021-08-19 18:45:45.310936'),
